      "text": "Found 5 files mentioning \"seedlegals\". Let me also check the broader pattern including PDF and other files. But first, let me read those 5 files to see the context. PDFs may contain text references but Select-String on PDFs requires extracting text first. Let me first read the .txt and .json files, then check the PDFs for keyword extraction.\n\nActually let me also expand the search to include other extensions (like .m4a transcripts — but those are audio). PDFs and other binary formats would need different tools. Let me focus on the 5 files found, and additionally try to extract text from a few likely PDFs like \"Spinout-Questionnaire.pdf\", \"Stage 1 Submission\", \"Startup Realities\", and the \"Interview With Antonio Dikele D...\" which look related.\n\nLet me first read the 5 found files to getthe content with seedlegals.",
