IS/EIS-friendly advance subscription agreement.\n\n[Get Started](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n£150 \\+ VAT\n\n### Seed & Series A Round\n\nPerfect for raising from £100k to £10m and beyond from angel investors and VCs.\n\n[Get Started](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n£1990 \\+ VAT\n\n### Instant Investment\n\nEasily top-up an existing round. We generate all the permissions and documents you need.\n\n[Get Started](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n£150 \\+ VAT\n\n### SeedNOTE\n\nInvestor looking for interest, return of capital? Our full-featured convertible note is for you.\n\n[Get Started](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n£1990 \\+ VAT\n\n### Bootstrap Round\n\nThe perfect way to raise up to £100k from Friends & Family.\n\n[Get Started](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n£990 \\+ VAT\n\n### Convert ASAs & CLNs\n\nConvert existing ASAs and CLNs into equity easily, straight from your Convertibles Table. No charge for SeedFAST or SeedNOTE.\n\n[Get Started](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n£\n\n## Funding\n\nThe launchpad for your raise. Get investor-ready, meet investors, close with confidence.\n\n-   ![Icon 4](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-4.svg) Sort **SEIS/EIS** quickly with **free Advance Assurance or Compliance**\n-   ![Icon 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-2.svg) **Accelerate funding round negotiations** with a clear, investor-ready term sheet\n-   ![Icon 3 1](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-3-1.svg) Work with **an experienced funding round expert** to shape your raise\n-   ![Icon 3 1](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-3-1.svg) Get help from your **dedicated account manager** and **priority platform support**\n-   ![Icon 3](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-3.svg) Save more with **discounted Flex credits** across SeedFASTs, rounds, Instant Investment\n-   ![Icon 3](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-3.svg) Reach out to investors and **get your SEIS/EIS faster** with a **£100 discount** on SeedLegals Boost\n-   ![Icon 3](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-3.svg) Get **priority access** to SeedLegals events and our founder WhatsApp community\n-   ![Icon 5](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Icon-5.svg) Includes everything in Access\n\n**Raising and hiring?** Pay less when you buy both Funding and Options together\n\n£1,199 / year + VAT\n\n[\n\nGet started\n\n](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n[\n\nBook a call\n\n](/talk-to-an-expert/ )\n\n![Dashboard Interface](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Funding@2x.png)\n\nCompare plans\n\nAccess\n\nFunding\n\nOptions\n\nDay-to-day legals\n\nCap table management  (unlimited shareholders)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nTeam and employment agreements\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nEssential contracts and policies\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nBoard documents\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.c