p-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\nOptions\n\nUnlimited EMI valuations\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nUnlimited EMI option schemes\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nUnlimited Unapproved option schemes\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nUnlimited option grants\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nEmployee dashboard\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\nOptions calculator\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Not included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/cross-v2.svg)\n\n![Included](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/pricing-v4/tick-v2.svg)\n\n![Header Icon](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/header-icon.svg)\n\n## \n\nChoose the bolt-ons that suit your business\n\n## Get investment-ready\n\nGet SEIS/EIS right, quickly – and help your investors unlock valuable tax relief.\n\n## How much will my funding round cost?\n\nUK company UK\n\nNon-UK company Non-UK\n\nNominee company Nominee\n\n#### SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance\n\nGet a fully compliant, expert checked application to ensure a speedy approval from HMRC.\n\n£499\n\n\\+ VAT\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Feature-flag-2-1.png)\n\n#### SEIS/EIS Compliance\n\nEasily give your investors what they need to claim their tax deductions post funding.\n\nFrom\n\n£599\n\nadd £500 +VAT if no prior Advance Assurance  \nadd £500 +VAT if the funding round was not on SeedLegals  \nadd £500 +VAT for a nominee entity\n\n\\+ VAT\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Group-1.png)\n\n#### SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance\n\nFor foreign companies. Get expert support to offer eligible UK investors valuable tax relief.\n\n£990\n\n\\+ VAT (if applicable)\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Group-2.png)\n\n#### SEIS/EIS Compliance\n\nFor foreign companies. Give your UK investors what they need to claim tax benefits post funding.\n\nFrom\n\n£990\n\nadd £500 + VAT if no prior Advance Assurance\n\n\\+ VAT (if applicable)  \nIncludes unlimited SEIS3 certificates\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Group-1.png)\n\n#### SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance\n\nFor nominee structures. Get expert support to offer grouped investors valuable tax relief.\n\n£490\n\n\\+ VAT\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Group-2.png)\n\n#### SEIS/EIS Compliance\n\nFor nominee structures. Give your grouped investors what they need to claim tax benefits post funding.\n\nFrom\n\n£990\n\nadd 500 + VAT if no prior Advance Assurance  \nadd 500 + VAT if the funding round was not on SeedLegals\n\n\\+ VAT  \nIf the funding round was on SeedLegals\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Group-1.png)\n\n## Find investors\n\nGet your pitch in front of active investors and show you’re ready to raise with strong foundations in place.\n\n#### Boost ![icon](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/new.png)\n\nRaise faster with the brilliant package that helps you reach out to the right investors, shows investors your company is set up properly to raise and strengthens your SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance application.\n\n£649\n\n\\+ VAT\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Group-5.png)\n\n## Manage cap table updates\n\nKeep your ownership clean and accurate.\n\n#### Rollup\n\nEasily roll up smaller investors into one entry on your share register, for a cleaner cap table.\n\n£2,490\n\n+VAT\n\nFree to start, pay on completion\n\n#### Issue shares\n\nIssue free shares to new team members, directors and advisors. Usually before a first funding round.\n\n£299\n\n\\+ VAT\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Feature-flag-3.png)\n\n#### Transfer Shares\n\nInvestor, founder or team member looking to sell their shares? We'll build all the documents you need.\n\n£299\n\n\\+ VAT per transfer\n\n![Custom](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/Feature-flag-1-1.png)\n\n## Grow your business\n\nUnlock more runway and get the legal support you need to scale.\n\n[\n\n#### R&D Tax Relief\n\nEverything you need to claim your R&D tax credit from HMRC. Including 4 hours of external specialist enquiry support.\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/rd-tax-credit-claim/)\n\nOpening fee\n\n£1,490\n\n\\+ VAT (non-refundable)\n\nDiscounted opening fee of £499 + VAT on Funding & Options plans\n\nClosing fee\n\n5%\n\nR&D claims opened within a month of their statutory deadline:\n\n10% of R&D tax benefit + VAT\n\n£3,000 + VAT minimum\n\n\\+ VAT (minimum £1,000 + VAT)\n\nPaid on completion of work. Refundable, pro-rata or in full, if the claim is rejected in part or in full.\n\n#### General Counsel as a Service\n\nGet 10 hours of expert legal support for £2,999 from a dedicated senior lawyer to support with commercial and employment contracts, IP, data privacy and more.  \n  \n  \nGet more hours and even better rates by purchasing our 25 hour pack for £4,999. Top-ups available when needed.\n\nFrom\n\n£2,999\n\n\\+ VAT\n\n## Sell your company\n\nInstantly create every agreement with every term exactly how you want it.\n\n[\n\n#### Exit\n\n...288 lines truncated...\n\nThe tool call succeeded but the output was truncated. Full output saved to: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.local\\share\\opencode\\tool-output\\tool_ef441e374001KMOGNS1CNGsCzn\nUse the Task tool to have explore agent process this file with Grep and Read (with offset/limit). Do NOT read the full file yourself - delegate to save context.",
