      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Great, I got the full SeedLegals pricing page. Let me extract the key info:\n\n**SeedLegals current pricing (2026, as of June):**\n- **Access plan**: £649/year + VAT (annual) — day-to-day legals, cap table, agreements, data room\n- **Funding plan**: £1,199/year + VAT (when bought alone), or £549/year + VAT (bundled with Access via Boost)\n- **Options plan**: £2,699/year + VAT (EMI options, valuations)\n- **Combined Funding + Options**: when bought together, less\n\n**Pay-as-you-go (Flex):**\n- SeedFAST: £150 + VAT\n- Instant Investment: £150 + VAT\n- Seed & Series A Round: £1990 + VAT\n- SeedNOTE: £1990 + VAT\n- Bootstrap Round: £990 + VAT\n- Convert ASAs & CLNs: £0\n\n**Bolt-ons:**\n- SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance: £499 + VAT (one free with Funding plan)\n- SEIS/EIS Compliance: from £599 + VAT\n- Issue shares: £299 + VAT\n- Transfer Shares: £299 + VAT per transfer\n- Boost: £649 + VAT (or £549 with Funding plan)\n- Rollup: £2,490 + VAT (free to start)\n- R&D Tax Relief: opening fee £1,490 + VAT (£499 + VAT if on Funding & Options plans), closing fee 5%\n- General Counsel: from £2,999 + VAT\n\nThe \"Start Free\" button suggests there's a free tier to begin with. Let me look for webhook integration now. I need to search for that. Alsoneed to find cheaper alternatives.\n\nLet me also check for the SeedLegals developer docs / API page.",
