s.com/en/seis-eis?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/SeedFAST.png)\n\n### SeedFAST / SeedNOTE\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/seedfast-seednote?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/FundingRound.png)\n\n### Funding Rounds\n\nFrom Boostrap, Seed Rounds all the way to Series A\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/funding-rounds?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/InstantInvest-V3%20(1).png)\n\n### Instant Investment\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/instant-investment?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/Board.png)\n\n### Board of Directors and Company Governance\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/board-of-directors-and-company-governance?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/Options.png)\n\n### Options and Option Schemes\n\nOptions, EMI & Unapproved Schemes\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/options-and-option-schemes?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/R%26D.png)\n\n### R&D Tax Credits\n\nCapture your R&D claims on SeedLegals guided by our R&D tax credit specialists\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/rd-tax-credits?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/Team%20agreements.png)\n\n### Team, Agreements & Policies\n\nFounder, Employee, Advisor, Consultancy and more!\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/team-agreements-policies?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/Deal%20manager.png)\n\n### Investors & Deal Manager\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/investors-deal-manager?hsLang=en)\n\n[\n\n![](https://help.seedlegals.com/hubfs/Accelerators.png)\n\n### Accelerators\n\n\n\n](https://help.seedlegals.com/en/accelerators?hsLang=en)\n\n-   [Blog](https://seedlegals.com/resources/?nr=1)\n\n[![Chill listening crop-3](https://help.seedlegals.com/hs-fs/hubfs/favicon.png?width=24&height=24&name=favicon.png \"Chill listening crop-3\")](//seedlegals.com)\n\nSeedLegals\n\n[](https://www.