ewsletter\n    \n    Never miss a beat with exclusive updates and invites\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/meetings/investor-newsletter/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Meet the team\n    \n    See how SeedLegals helps streamline your investments\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/meetings/investor-interest/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ![Navigation Ad Book A Call Investor](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Navigation-ad_Book-a-call_Investor.jpg)\n    \n    Get deals done faster\n    \n    Explore our all-in-one platform: seamless deal flow, simplified investments, portfolio management and legal support.\n    \n    Book a demo\n    \n    \n    \n    ](/meetings/investor-interest/)\n    \n-   [\n    \n    Pricing\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/pricing/)\n    \n-   [\n    \n    Resources\n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    Insights\n    \n    [\n    \n    Articles\n    \n    Must-have insights from industry experts, founders and investors\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/resources/)[\n    \n    Reports\n    \n    Expert analysis on trends we see from our data\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/reports/)[\n    \n    Termometer\n    \n    The UK's most detailed analysis of early-stage funding deal terms\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/termometer/)\n    \n    Categories:\n    \n    [— SEIS/EIS](/resources/category/seis-eis/)\n    \n    [— Funding](/resources/category/funding-guides/)\n    \n    [— Options](/resources/category/share-option-schemes/)\n    \n    [— R&D](/resources/category/r-and-d-tax-credits/)\n    \n    [— Deal Data](/resources/category/deal-data/)\n    \n    [— News](/resources/category/news/)\n    \n    [— Investor Hub](/resources/category/investor-directory/)\n    \n    Guides\n    \n    [\n    \n    Ebooks\n    \n    Get the ultimate startup starter kit\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/)[\n    \n    Checklists\n    \n    Ace the admin with step-by-step guidance\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/checklists/)[\n    \n    Videos\n    \n    NEW\n    \n    Catch up on webinars and learn from specialists\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/videos/)\n    \n    Community\n    \n    [\n    \n    Events\n    \n    ](/events/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Newsletter\n    \n    ](/newsletters/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Case Studies\n    \n    ](/customers/)\n    \n    Support\n    \n    [Help Centre](https://help.seedlegals.com/en)\n    \n    [Speak to our experts](/talk-to-an-expert/)\n    \n    [SeedLegals Academy](https://seedlegals.com/seedlegals-academy/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ![Pitch Deck Template Download PRebiew image](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Pitch-deck-template-download.png)\n    \n    Nail your pitch and impress investors\n    \n    Get the pitch deck that’s helping 3,500+ founders raise. 12 customisable slides, plus insider tips from investors.\n    \n    Get the pitch deck\n    \n    \n    \n    ](/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n    \n-   [\n    \n    Company\n    \n    ](#)\n    -   [\n        \n        ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/about.svg)\n        \n        ##### About us\n        \n        SeedLegals is the one-stop platform for the legals you need to get funded and grow your business.\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/about/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Mission & values\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/about/mission-values/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Careers\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/careers/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Partners\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/partners-community/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Contact\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/contact/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Media\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/media/)\n\n[Start Free](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\nAlready have an account? [Log in](https://app.seedlegals.com/login)\n\n[](https://www.facebook.com/seedlegals)[](https://twitter.com/seedlegals)[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/15088107/)[](https://www.instagram.com/seedlegals/)\n\n![1 (4)](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/1-4.webp)\n\nGet SEIS/EIS ready. [**Download our free guide to an HMRC-friendly pitch deck**](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/seis-eis-pitch-deck-guide/).\n\n[Download now](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/seis-eis-pitch-deck-guide/)\n\n[](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/seis-eis-pitch-deck-guide/)\n\n![Group 2609265](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Group-2609265.webp)\n\nPitch Perfect: **[Get the pitch deck template investors want you to use.](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)**\n\n[Download now](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n\n[](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n\n![Tips From Investors Ebook](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Tips-from-investors-eBook.webp)\n\nGet investment-ready! [**Get our best tips from active investors.**](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/tips-from-investors/)\n\n[Download now](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/tips-from-investors/)\n\n[](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/tips-from-investors/)\n\n[![SeedLegals Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/seedlegals-logo.svg)](/)\n\nFor Founders\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/start-icon.svg)\n\nStart\n\nHire your team and get investment ready\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/)\n\n[\n\nEssential Startup Contracts\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/legal-documents/)\n\n[\n\nFounder Agreements\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)\n\n[\n\nRegister a company\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/register-a-company/)\n\n[\n\nTeam Agreements\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/)\n\n[\n\nApply for SEIS & EIS\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/seis-eis/)\n\n[\n\nCap Table\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/cap-table/)\n\n[\n\nStaff Handbook\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/staff-handbook/)\n\n[\n\nCompany Policies\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/company-policies/)\n\n[\n\nPartner Perks\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/marketplace/)\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/raise-icon.svg)\n\nRaise\n\nTake care of everything you need to close investment.\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/)\n\n[\n\nPitch to Investors\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/pitch/)\n\n[\n\nSeedLegals Boost\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/boost/)\n\n[\n\nRaise Before a Round\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-before-a-round/)\n\n[\n\nDo a Funding Round\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-a-round/)\n\n[\n\nFinance for Fundraising\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/finance-for-fundraising/)\n\n[\n\nLegal Advice for a Round\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/)\n\n[\n\nInstant Investment\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/top-up-a-round/)\n\n[\n\nSEIS/EIS Compliance\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/seis-eis-compliance/)\n\n[\n\nData Room\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/data-room/)\n\n[\n\nRollup\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/raise/rollup/)\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/grow-icon.svg)\n\nGrow\n\nManage shareholders and reward your team with equity.\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/)\n\n[\n\nShare Option Schemes\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/)\n\n[\n\nEMI Option Schemes\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-option-schemes/)\n\n[\n\nEMI Valuation\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-valuation/)\n\n[\n\nUnapproved Option Schemes\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/unapproved/)\n\n[\n\nR&D Tax Credits\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/rd-tax-credit-claim/)\n\n[\n\nLegal Advisory Service\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/general-counsel/)\n\n[\n\nShare Transfers\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-transfers/)\n\n[\n\nManage your board\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/board-management/)\n\n[\n\nUSA Expansion\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/usa-expansion/)\n\n[\n\nDelaware Flip\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/delaware-flip/)\n\n[\n\nFlip & Raise\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/flip-raise/)\n\n[\n\nSell your company\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/exit/)\n\n[\n\n![Navigation Ad Book A Call Founder](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Navigation-ad_Book-a-call_Founder.jpg)\n\nGrow faster with SeedLegals\n\nFrom getting started to getting funded, we provide the mission-critical support you need to scale your business.\n\nBook a demo\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/talk-to-an-expert/)\n\n[\n\nFor Investors\n\n\n\n](/investors/)\n\n[\n\n![Icon handshake](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/angel-investors.svg)\n\nCreate a syndicate\n\nGet together with other investors and invest as a group.\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/investors/syndicate/)[\n\n![Icon bag of money](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/vc-fund.svg)\n\nRun your deal\n\nStreamline deals with tailored proposals via traditional rounds or agile tools.\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/investors/deal-manager/)[\n\n![Seis For Investors Icon](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/seis-for-investors-icon.svg)\n\nGet SEIS/EIS relief\n\nGet SEIS/EIS tax relief certificates quickly and accurately with the help of our experts.\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/investors/investor-seis/)[\n\n![Exit Modelling](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/exit-modelling.svg)\n\nManage your portfolio\n\nSee up-to-date shareholding and model exit scenarios.\n\n](/investors/exit-modelling/)\n\nLearn and connect\n\n[\n\nArticles\n\nGain insights from our team, investors and industry experts\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/investor-hub/)\n\n[\n\nAngel investor course\n\nSign up to our free 5-day video course on angel investing\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/investors/angel-investor-course/)\n\n[\n\nNewsletter\n\nNever miss a beat with exclusive updates and invites\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/meetings/investor-newsletter/)\n\n[\n\nMeet the team\n\nSee how SeedLegals helps streamline your investments\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/meetings/investor-interest/)\n\n[\n\n![Navigation Ad Book A Call Investor](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Navigation-ad_Book-a-call_Investor.jpg)\n\nGet deals done faster\n\nExplore our all-in-one platform: seamless deal flow, simplified investments, portfolio management and legal support.\n\nBook a demo\n\n\n\n](/meetings/investor-interest/)\n\n[\n\nPricing\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/pricing/)\n\n[\n\nResources\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/)\n\nInsights\n\n[\n\nArticles\n\nMust-have insights from industry experts, founders and investors\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/)[\n\nReports\n\nExpert analysis on trends we see from our data\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/reports/)[\n\nTermometer\n\nThe UK's most detailed analysis of early-stage funding deal terms\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/termometer/)\n\nCategories:\n\n[— SEIS/EIS](/resources/category/seis-eis/)\n\n[— Funding](/resources/category/funding-guides/)\n\n[— Options](/resources/category/share-option-schemes/)\n\n[— R&D](/resources/category/r-and-d-tax-credits/)\n\n[— Deal Data](/resources/category/deal-data/)\n\n[— News](/resources/category/news/)\n\n[— Investor Hub](/resources/category/investor-directory/)\n\nGuides\n\n[\n\nEbooks\n\nGet the ultimate startup starter kit\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/)[\n\nChecklists\n\nAce the admin with step-by-step guidance\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/checklists/)[\n\nVideos\n\nNEW\n\nCatch up on webinars and learn from specialists\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/videos/)\n\nCommunity\n\n[\n\nEvents\n\n](/events/)\n\n[\n\nNewsletter\n\n](/newsletters/)\n\n[\n\nCase Studies\n\n](/customers/)\n\nSupport\n\n[Help Centre](https://help.seedlegals.com/en)\n\n[Speak to our experts](/talk-to-an-expert/)\n\n[SeedLegals Academy](https://seedlegals.com/seedlegals-academy/)\n\n[\n\n![Pitch Deck Template Download PRebiew image](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Pitch-deck-template-download.png)\n\nNail your pitch and impress investors\n\nGet the pitch deck that’s helping 3,500+ founders raise. 12 customisable slides, plus insider tips from investors.\n\nGet the pitch deck\n\n\n\n](/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n\nCompany\n\n-   [\n    \n    ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/about.svg)\n    \n    About us\n    \n    SeedLegals is the one-stop platform for the legals you need to get funded and grow your business.\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/about/)\n-   [Mission & values](https://seedlegals.com/about/mission-values/)\n-   [Careers](https://seedlegals.com/careers/)\n-   [Partners](https://seedlegals.com/partners-community/)\n-   [Contact](https://seedlegals.com/contact/)\n-   [Media](https://seedlegals.com/media/)\n\n![en](/wp-content/uploads/flags/en.png)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/lang-selector-chev.svg)\n\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/fr.png)FR](https://seedlegals.com/fr/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/us.png)US](https://seedlegals.com/us/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/ie.png)IE](https://seedlegals.com/ie/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/hk.png)HK](https://seedlegals.com/hk/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/sg.png)SG](https://seedlegals.com/sg/?nr=1)\n\n[+44 20 4587 5701](tel:+442045875701)\n\n[Login](https://app.seedlegals.com/login)\n\n[Start Free](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n-   [Raise](https://seedlegals.com/raise/) Data Room\n\n[Register a company](https://seedlegals.com/start/register-a-company/)\n\n# Data Room included in all SeedLegals memberships\n\n## The secure way to store and share your legal documents\n\n✔ Upload confidential documents to your virtual Data Room  \n✔ Control access through custom groups  \n✔ Change permissions at any time for unlimited users\n\n[\n\nTalk to an expert\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mathieu-Henry-1-1-300x300.jpeg)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Raphaelle-Marquet-1-1-300x300.jpeg)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Marc-Fournier-1-1-300x300.jpeg)\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/talk-to-an-expert/)[Start free](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n[4.9 out of five star rating on Trustpilot](https://uk.trustpilot.com/review/www.seedlegals.com?utm_medium=trustbox&utm_source=Horizontal)\n\n[\n\nTrustpilot\n\n](https://uk.trustpilot.com/review/www.seedlegals.com?utm_medium=trustbox&utm_source=Horizontal)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Data-Room.png)\n\n-   ## 60,000+\n    \n    companies use SeedLegals\n    \n-   ## £2.5b\n    \n    raised on SeedLegals\n    \n-   ## UK #1\n    \n    closer of funding rounds\n    \n-   ## 500,000+\n    \n    documents created and signed\n    \n\n![Shape](/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/shapes/circle.svg)\n\n###### Deal Data Room for your funding round\n\n## Use the Deal Data Room for secure due diligence\n\nSpeed up due diligence and make [funding](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-a-round/) faster. Share classified documents with investors, lawyers and advisors.\n\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Store all the sensitive documents for your investment round in one place\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Create groups to customise who can see what, and change access at any time\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Update everything in real time and manage securely on the cloud\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Funding-documents.png)\n\n###### Data Room for your Pitch to investors\n\n## Share information easily with potential investors\n\nNo need to send emails with large file attachments or force investors to download files. Your [Pitch](https://seedlegals.com/raise/pitch/) page comes with its own secure Data Room.\n\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Upload sensitive info such as financial forecasts\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Share in one click with interested investors\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Keep everything in one place - clean and clutter-free\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Pitch-data-room.png)\n\n![Shape](/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/shapes/circle.svg)\n\n###### Data Room for your board meetings\n\n## Create, share and manage board documents\n\nBye bye bulky [board](https://seedlegals.com/board-management/) pack. Data Room is the easy way to give everyone the access they need to company information.\n\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Get secure shared access for paperless meetings\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Give all your board members consistent, up-to-date information\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Build and share templated minutes for board meetings\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Board-meeting-data-room.png)\n\n![Shape](/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/shapes/circle.svg)\n\n###### Unlimited support with your Data Room\n\n## Chat online anytime with our experts\n\nNot sure how to access the Data Room or what files to add? If you have questions about Data Room, our expert team is here to help.\n\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Talk to us your way - chat, phone, email, video call\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Unlimited help included in all memberships - no extra cost\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Ask us anything - we're here 9am to 6pm Monday to Friday\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Speak-to-our-experts.png)\n\n## More resources\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/hero_data-room.png)\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/seedlegals-launches-deal-data-room/)\n\n[\n\nGet ready for due diligence with Deal Data Room\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/seedlegals-launches-deal-data-room/)\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/hero_pitch-investors-1-click-1.png)\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-to-investors-in-one-click/)\n\n[\n\nSend your Pitch in one click\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-to-investors-in-one-click/ )\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/5bbf7fc65211f4cc5df92887_Startup-Lawyer-Header-600x599@2x.jpg)\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/25-steps-funding/)\n\n[\n\nHow to complete your first funding round\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/25-steps-funding/)\n\n## FAQs\n\nGot questions about Data Room? We have the answers.\n\n  \n\n-   What is a data room?\n    \n    A data room is a secure online space where files can only be accessed with the correct authorisation. Startups use data rooms to share confidential documents with investors, potential investors, advisors or board members.  \n      \n    The benefit of a digital data room (sometimes called a virtual data room) is that it’s simple to share the link and give access - and to manage who is allowed to see sensitive information.\n    \n-   Where can I store documents on SeedLegals?\n    \n    All of the documents you create on the SeedLegals platform stay there securely. You can access them either within the workflow you used to create them (eg, to find your Term Sheet, go to **Raise** > **Funding Round** > **Data Room**) or through the **My Documents** tab.  \n      \n    You can also upload supporting documents to your Pitch Data Room, the Deal Data Room within your funding round, or to your Board Data Room.\n    \n-   How much does SeedLegals Data Room cost?\n    \n    There’s no extra charge for SeedLegals members to use our Data Rooms - and there’s no limit to the amount of users you can add. With a [Standard or Plus subscription](https://seedlegals.com/pricing/), you get full access to the Board and Pitch Data Rooms.  \n      \n    There’s no separate fee to use the Deal Data Room, but you will need to open a funding round. You can see full details on our [Pricing](https://seedlegals.com/pricing/) page.  \n      \n    There are plenty of online services available that offer digital data rooms, costing from £20 a month to hundreds of pounds a year per user. But on SeedLegals, you can securely store and share your documents, all on the same platform as you use to create them - and at no extra cost.\n    \n-   If my SeedLegals membership expires, will I lose all my documents?\n    \n    We want to make it easy for you to access your documents whenever you need them. If you cancel your membership, we’ll continue to safely store your documents for a period of time, so you can find them easily when you rejoin.  \n      \n    But please be aware that, under our [Terms of Service](https://seedlegals.com/terms-of-service/#8.-term-and-termination), we can’t guarantee that we’ll store your data forever. We recommend that you download all your documents and data before cancelling your membership.\n    \n-   Can I download all of my documents at once from SeedLegals?\n    \n    Yes. Go to **Settings** (bottom left of the platform menu), go across to **Display** and scroll to the bottom. You’ll see the option to download a ZIP file of all documents relating to your company, excluding certificates.  \n      \n    You can download Share and Note Certificates by going to the **Shares** tab in the platform menu, and choosing **Share Certificates** and **Note Certificates**.  \n    \n-   Can I access the Deal Data Room without a funding round?\n    \n    No, you can only access the Deal Data Room within a funding round. You can see full details on our [Pricing](https://seedlegals.com/pricing/) page.\n    \n-   How do I use the Deal Data Room?\n    \n    Go to **Raise** and click on into your open funding round, then click the **Documents** tab. You’ll see all the documents you’ve created on SeedLegals for your round at the top and underneath that is your Deal Data Room where you can upload your own documents. You can see more information in this [Deal Data Room article](https://seedlegals.com/resources/seedlegals-launches-deal-data-room/).\n    \n-   How do I customise access permissions for the Deal Data Room?\n    \n    We created Groups to make it easy to share sets of documents with dynamic and custom groups. In your funding round, click the **Groups** tab to view and manage your groups.  \n      \n    Dynamic groups include **All investors** – this group contains all the investors you’ve added to your round.  \n      \n    Adding a new investor? All documents in that sharing group are automatically shared with them. Investor pulls out? Just remove them from the round, and their sharing permissions are automatically removed.  \n      \n    Or go ahead to create your own custom groups, for example:  \n    \\- Lead investors and their lawyers  \n    \\- ‘Maybe’ and ‘Confirmed’ investors\n    \n-   What kind of documents go in the Deal Data Room?\n    \n    When you do a funding round, VC investors will have an extensive checklist for their due diligence covering many aspects of your business from tax, finance and legal to your IT, sales and marketing systems and statistics.  \n      \n    The documents investors will often ask to see include:  \n    \\- [Founder Service Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)  \n    \\- [Employment Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/employment-agreement/) for your key team members  \n    \\- Contracts with third parties  \n    \\- [IP Assignment Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/ip-assignment/)  \n    \\- Your [five year business plan](https://seedlegals.com/resources/5-year-business-plan/) and financial forecasts  \n      \n    With the SeedLegals Deal Data Room, it’s easy to upload all the documents you need, add more at any time, and share access to them securely.\n    \n-   How are my documents and data protected?\n    \n    We take the security of your documents and data very seriously and take various steps and measures to protect it.  \n      \n    Here are just some of the ways we make sure your data is secure:  \n      \n    \\- We’ll never share or make your data or information available to anyone without your explicit permission (other than being legally required such as by a court order)  \n    \\- Your data is uploaded and downloaded over a secure connection, and your credentials are encrypted and hashed. We don’t store (or even know) your password  \n    \\- Only people you’ve assigned as members of your team can access your data, and you can assign specific permissions to individual team members  \n      \n    You can read our full Data Protection Policy here in our [Terms of Service](https://seedlegals.com/terms-of-service/).\n    \n\n## You’re in safe hands\n\nOur team of legal and funding experts have helped thousands of entrepreneurs raise money and grow their businesses.\n\n-   ##### Beautifully organised\n    \n    Your company's core agreements, all in one place\n    \n-   ##### Secure signatures\n    \n    Share and collect signatures online via SeedLegals\n    \n-   ##### Backed by real lawyers\n    \n    Create the exact documents you need at every stage of growth\n    \n-   ##### Serious about security\n    \n    Your information stays safe and confidential in our secure system\n    \n-   ##### Helpful humans\n    \n    Talk to one of our friendly team anytime on live chat\n    \n-   ##### Extra protection\n    \n    Don't worry, our insurance covers claims related to our platform\n    \n\n## We’ve helped over 60,000\n\ncompanies\n\nFrom food to FinTech and beyond, join thousands of startups who use SeedLegals to start, raise and grow faster.\n\n-   ![Yoller](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Yoller-e1574964551789.png)\n-   ![Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/logo.png)\n-   ![Pluto 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Pluto-2-e1573751477232.png)\n-   ![The Family 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/The-family-2.png)\n-   ![Trim It](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/trim-it-w-e1590253311428.png)\n-   ![Oddbox Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/oddbox-logo-e1573757173841.png)\n\n[More customer stories](/customers/)\n\n-   ![Louise Doherty](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Louise-Doherty.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    The reality is you’re on a journey; fundraising is so much about the narrative. SeedLegals allows you to tell the right story at the right time with the right legal documents for different types of investors.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Louise Doherty\n    \n    Founder & CEO, Yoller\n    \n    ![Yoller](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Yoller-e1574964551789.png)\n    \n-   ![Qure](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Qure-e1573739439847.png)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    SeedLegals held our hand through complex investor negotiations and even picked up on some errors produced by our previous lawyers which were a well-known City law firm!\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Alex Templeton\n    \n    Founder & CEO, Qured\n    \n    ![Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/logo.png)\n    \n-   ![Pluto](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/PLuto-e1573751551277.png)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    One of the great things about SeedLegals is that it is designed to be appropriate for the round and the stage of the business. They keep it simple. It feels like they really understand that.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Alex Rainey\n    \n    Co-founder & CEO, Pluto\n    \n    ![Pluto 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Pluto-2-600x600.png)\n    \n-   ![Thefamily](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/thefamily.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    How do I get all the businesses I invest in to use SeedLegals?\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Alexander Wyndham\n    \n    Angel Investor , The Family\n    \n    ![The Family 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/The-family-2.png)\n    \n-   ![Darren Trimit](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Darren-Trimit.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    It's easy to forget about the legal side of things but SeedLegals make things really easy to understand. The team at SeedLegals are truly amazing.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Darren Tenkorang\n    \n    Founder, TRIM-IT\n    \n    ![Trim It](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/trim-it-w-600x329.png)\n    \n-   ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Oddbox-founders.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    There’s an opportunity to reach a specialist advisor via chat, phone and email to check in on anything. The SeedLegals team were extremely responsive – really amazing.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Emilie Vanpoperinghe\n    \n    Co-Founder, OddBox\n    \n    ![Oddbox Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/oddbox-logo-600x229.png)\n    \n\n-   ![Yoller](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Yoller-e1574964551789.png)\n-   ![Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/logo.png)\n-   ![Pluto 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Pluto-2-e1573751477232.png)\n-   ![The Family 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/The-family-2.png)\n-   ![Trim It](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/trim-it-w-e1590253311428.png)\n-   ![Oddbox Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/oddbox-logo-e1573757173841.png)\n\n[\n\n#### Funding Guides\n\nTools, resources and expert advice to help you close your next investment.\n\nLearn more\n\n![Funding Guides](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/funding-guides.svg)\n\n](/resources/category/funding-guides/)[\n\n#### Find Investors\n\nFind the perfect investor for your round. We've compiled lists of the most active investors in each sector and region.\n\nLearn more\n\n![Investor Database](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/investor-database.svg)\n\n](/resources/category/investor-directory/)\n\n## Start your journey with us\n\n[Start free](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)[\n\nTalk to an expert\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Mathieu-Henry-1-1-300x300.jpeg)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Raphaelle-Marquet-1-1-300x300.jpeg)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Marc-Fournier-1-1-300x300.jpeg)\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/talk-to-an-expert/)\n\n-   ![Beulah](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Beulah-e1574188143996.png)\n-   ![Brolly](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/brolly-e1574187797542.png)\n-   ![Oddbox Transparent](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/OddBox-transparent-e1574187825770.png)\n-   ![Index Ventures](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Index-ventures-1-e1574189344246.png)\n-   ![Seedcamp](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/seedcamp.png)\n-   ![Qured](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Qured-1-scaled-e1574188257782.png)\n\n![SeedLegal's Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/sl-logo-drop.svg)\n\n### Startups made easy. Sorted.\n\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/fr.png)FR](https://seedlegals.com/fr/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/us.png)US](https://seedlegals.com/us/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/ie.png)IE](https://seedlegals.com/ie/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/hk.png)HK](https://seedlegals.com/hk/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/sg.png)SG](https://seedlegals.com/sg/?nr=1)\n\n##### [Start\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/)\n\n[Essential Startup Contracts](https://seedlegals.com/legal-documents/)\n\n[Founder Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)\n\n[Register a company](https://seedlegals.com/start/register-a-company/)\n\n[Team Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/)\n\n[SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance](https://seedlegals.com/start/seis-eis/)\n\n[Cap Table](https://seedlegals.com/start/cap-table/)\n\n[Staff Handbook](https://seedlegals.com/staff-handbook/)\n\n[Company Policies](https://seedlegals.com/grow/company-policies/)\n\n[Partner Perks](https://seedlegals.com/marketplace/)\n\n##### [Raise\n\n](/raise/)\n\n[Pitch to Investors](https://seedlegals.com/raise/pitch/)\n\n[SeedLegals Boost](https://seedlegals.com/raise/boost/)\n\n[Raise Before a Round](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-before-a-round/)\n\n[Do a Funding Round](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-a-round/)\n\n[Do a Series A Round](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-series-a-round/)\n\n[Legal Advice for a Round](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/)\n\n[Instant Investment](https://seedlegals.com/raise/top-up-a-round/)\n\n[SEIS/EIS Compliance](https://seedlegals.com/raise/seis-eis-compliance/)\n\n[Data Room](https://seedlegals.com/raise/data-room/)\n\n[Finance for Fundraising](https://seedlegals.com/raise/finance-for-fundraising/)\n\n##### [Grow\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/)\n\n[Share Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/)\n\n[EMI Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-option-schemes/)\n\n[EMI Valuation](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-valuation/)\n\n[Unapproved Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/unapproved/)\n\n[R&D Tax Credits](https://seedlegals.com/grow/rd-tax-credit-claim/)\n\n[R&D Tax Credit Calculator](https://seedlegals.com/rd-calculator/)\n\n[Legal Advisory Service](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/general-counsel/)\n\n[Share Transfers](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-transfers/)\n\n[Manage your board](https://seedlegals.com/board-management/)\n\n[USA Expansion](https://seedlegals.com/grow/usa-expansion/)\n\n[Delaware Flip](https://seedlegals.com/grow/delaware-flip/)\n\n[Flip & Raise](https://seedlegals.com/grow/flip-raise/)\n\n[Sell your company](https://seedlegals.com/grow/exit/)\n\n##### [Investors\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/investors/)\n\n[Create a syndicate](/investors/syndicate/)\n\n[Run your deal](/investors/deal-manager/)\n\n[Get SEIS/EIS relief](/investors/investor-seis/)\n\n[Manage your portfolio](/investors/exit-modelling/)\n\n##### Resources\n\n[Startup Guides](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/startup-guides/)\n\n[Funding Guides](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/funding-guides/)\n\n[SEIS EIS](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/seis-eis/)\n\n[Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/share-option-schemes/)\n\n[R&D Guides](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/r-and-d-tax-credits/)\n\n[Termometer](https://seedlegals.com/termometer/)\n\n[Deal Data](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/deal-data/)\n\n[Checklists](https://seedlegals.com/checklists/)\n\n[ebooks](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/)\n\n[Newsletters](https://seedlegals.com/newsletters/)\n\n[Find Investors](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/investor-directory/)\n\n[Investor Hub](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/investor-hub/)\n\n[Help Centre](https://help.seedlegals.com/en)\n\n[SeedLegals Academy](https://seedlegals.com/seedlegals-academy/)\n\n##### [About\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/about/)\n\n[Mission & values](https://seedlegals.com/about/mission-values/)\n\n[Partners Community](https://seedlegals.com/partners-community/)\n\n[Become a partner](https://seedlegals.com/partners/)\n\n[Our authors and experts](https://seedlegals.com/authors-and-experts/)\n\n[Case studies](https://seedlegals.com/customers/)\n\n[For Accountants](https://seedlegals.com/for-accountants/)\n\n[Events](https://seedlegals.com/events/)\n\n[Media](https://seedlegals.com/media/)\n\n© SeedLegals 2026. All Rights Reserved.\n\n[Privacy Policy](https://seedlegals.com/privacy-policy/) [Terms Of Service](https://seedlegals.com/terms-of-service/) [Cookie Policy](https://seedlegals.com/cookie-policy/) [Editorial Policy](https://seedlegals.com/editorial-policy/)\n\n [![facebook](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/facebook.svg)](https://www.facebook.com/seedlegals)[![twitter](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/x.svg) ](https://twitter.com/seedlegals)[![instagram](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/instagram.svg) ](https://www.instagram.com/seedlegals/)[![linkedin](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/linkedin.svg)](https://www.linkedin.com/company/15088107/)",
