-   [Partner programme](https://www.vestd.com/partner-programme)\n\n[Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/vestdhq/) [Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/company/vestd/mycompany/) [X](https://twitter.com/VestdHQ) [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/@VestdHQ) [Tiktok](https://www.tiktok.com/@vestd)\n\n##### The sharetech platform\n\nManage your equity and shareholders\n\n![Share schemes & options icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/piechart.svg)\n\nShare schemes & options\n\n[Give key people some skin in the game](https://www.vestd.com/employee-share-scheme)\n\n![Equity management icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/points.svg)\n\nEquity management\n\n[Powerful tools and automations](https://www.vestd.com/equity-management-software)\n\n![Start a business icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/rocket.svg)\n\nMigrate to Vestd\n\n[Digitise or move your existing scheme](https://www.vestd.com/migrate)\n\n![Company valuations icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/calculator.svg)\n\nCompany valuations\n\n[UK, US & international valuations](https://www.vestd.com/valuations)\n\n![Fundraising icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/crosshairs.svg)\n\nFundraising\n\n[InVestd Raise - 0% completion fees!](https://in.vestd.com/raise)\n\nFor all company sizes\n\n[Startups](https://www.vestd.com/growth-hub)\n\n[Scaleups & SMEs](https://www.vestd.com/sme-hub)\n\n[Enterprise](https://www.vestd.com/enterprise-hub)\n\nUse cases\n\n[Accountants](https://www.vestd.com/accountants)\n\n[Advisors](https://www.vestd.com/advisors)\n\n[CFOs & FDs](https://www.vestd.com/cfos)\n\n[Company Secretaries](https://www.vestd.com/share-scheme-software-for-company-secretaries)\n\n[Founders](https://www.vestd.com/founders)\n\n[HR teams](https://www.vestd.com/hr)\n\n[Investors](https://www.vestd.com/investors)\n\n[![EMI 500 top nav blue](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/EMI%20500%20top%20nav%20blue.png?width=317&height=317&name=EMI%20500%20top%20nav%20blue.png)](https://www.vestd.com/new-emi-rules-get-your-share-scheme-ready?utm_source=mega-menu&utm_medium=direct)\n\n##### The sharetech platform\n\nLaunch funds, evalute deals & invest\n\n![SPV icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/hub.svg)\n\nSpecial Purpose Vehicles (SPV)\n\n[Create a syndicate or fund](https://www.vestd.com/investors/syndicates)\n\n![Manage icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/briefcase.svg)\n\nPISCES\n\n[Liquidity for private companies](https://www.vestd.com/pisces)\n\n##### The sharetech platform\n\nPowerful tools and five-star support\n\n![Employee share schemes icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/piechart.svg)\n\nEmployee share schemes\n\n[Enterprise Management Incentives](https://www.vestd.com/emi-scheme)\n\n[Growth shares](https://www.vestd.com/growth-shares)\n\n[Unapproved options](https://www.vestd.com/unapproved-share-options)\n\n[CSOP](https://www.vestd.com/csops)\n\n[Digitise your scheme](https://www.vestd.com/digital-share-scheme)\n\n![Fundraising icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/crosshairs.svg)\n\nFundraising\n\n[Launch a funding round](https://in.vestd.com/raise)\n\n[S/EIS Advance Assurance](https://www.vestd.com/seis-eis-advance-assurance)\n\n[Create a data room](https://www.vestd.com/data-room)\n\n[Pitch deck template](https://www.vestd.com/free-pitch-deck-template)\n\n![Equity management icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/points.svg)\n\nEquity management\n\n[Cap table](https://www.vestd.com/cap-table)\n\n[Shareholder comms](https://www.vestd.com/shareholder-comms)\n\n[Shareholder dashboards](https://www.vestd.com/shareholder-dashboards)\n\n[Company secretarial tools](https://www.vestd.com/companies-house)\n\n[HRIS integration](https://www.vestd.com/hris-integration)\n\n![Starting up icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/rocket.svg)\n\nStarting up\n\n[Company incorporation](https://www.vestd.com/company-incorporation)\n\n[Co-founder equity](https://www.vestd.com/founder-equity)\n\n[Issue shares](https://www.vestd.com/issue-shares)\n\n[Business document templates](https://www.vestd.com/document-templates)\n\n[Share certificates](https://www.vestd.com/share-certificates)\n\n![Company valuations icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/calculator.svg)\n\nCompany valuations\n\n[Share scheme valuations](https://www.vestd.com/valuations)\n\n[409A valuations](https://www.vestd.com/409a-valuation)\n\n![Why Vestd icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/heart.svg)\n\nWhy Vestd?\n\n[Features](https://www.vestd.com/features)\n\n[Customer stories](https://www.vestd.com/learn/customers/)\n\n[Vestd vs other platforms](https://www.vestd.com/equity-management-buyers-guide)\n\n[Why choose Vestd?](https://www.vestd.com/key-benefits)\n\n##### The sharetech platform\n\nPredictable pricing and no hidden charges\n\n![Startups icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/rocket.svg)\n\nFor startups\n\n[Fundraising, share schemes & incorporation](https://www.vestd.com/pricing-startups)\n\n![SME icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/store.svg)\n\nFor scaleups & SMEs\n\n[Build and retain a winning team](https://www.vestd.com/pricing)\n\n![Enterprise icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/building.svg)\n\nFor larger companies\n\n[Streamline equity management](https://www.vestd.com/pricing-large)\n\n##### The sharetech platform\n\nIdeas, insight and tools to help you grow\n\n![Learn icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/reading.svg)\n\nLearn\n\n[About us](https://www.vestd.com/about)\n\n[Blog](https://www.vestd.com/blog)\n\n[Calculators](https://www.vestd.com/learn/calculators)\n\n[Guides & ebooks](https://www.vestd.com/learn/guides)\n\n[Newsroom](https://www.vestd.com/the-vestd-newsroom)\n\n[Resource library](https://www.vestd.com/resources)\n\n[Video library](https://www.vestd.com/videos)\n\n![Support icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/contact.svg)\n\nSupport\n\n[Contact us](https://www.vestd.com/contact)\n\n[Glossary](https://www.vestd.com/key-terms)\n\n[Help centre](https://www.vestd.com/help)\n\n[Key questions](https://www.vestd.com/key-questions)\n\n![Partners icon](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/mega-menu/support.svg)\n\nPartners\n\n[Our partners](https://www.vestd.com/partners-and-benefits)\n\n[Partner programme](https://www.vestd.com/partner-programme)\n\n[![top-nav-digitise-guide](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/top-nav-digitise-guide.jpg?width=350&height=350&name=top-nav-digitise-guide.jpg)](https://www.vestd.com/digitising-equity-management?utm_source=mega-menu&utm_medium=direct)\n\n# Plans for growing companies\n\n#### Build a winning team and unlock your potential\n\n[\n\nFor startups\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n](https://www.vestd.com/pricing-startups)\n\nFor scaleups & SMEs\n\n[\n\nFor larger companies\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n](https://www.vestd.com/pricing-large)\n\n![5035295-E20088](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/icons-e20088/5035295-E20088.svg)\n\nShare schemes\n\nDesign and launch a share scheme for your team, from £300 / month.\n\n![3552102-E20088](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/icons-e20088/3552102-E20088.svg)\n\nEquity management\n\nDigitally transform the way you monitor and manage ownership, to maintain compliance.\n\n![4250745-E20088](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/icons-e20088/4250745-E20088.svg)\n\nCompany secretarial\n\nAvoid filing docs and paperwork manually. The platform will do this automatically.\n\n![3555879-E20088](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/icons-e20088/3555879-E20088.svg)\n\nCompany valuations\n\nRequest up to date share scheme valuations for HMRC, or 409A valuations.\n\n### Request a demo\n\nAsk us anything about the platform via a free consultation from one of our experts.\n\n[Book a call](https://www.vestd.com/book-a-call-s0)\n\n![ratings-group-horizontal](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ratings-group-horizontal.png?width=405&height=122&name=ratings-group-horizontal.png)\n\n![Guy and Rachel at an event](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/guy-rachel-event-pic.jpg?width=555&height=380&name=guy-rachel-event-pic.jpg)\n\n##### Select an option below:\n\n-   Companies\n-   Investors\n-   Accountants\n\n## Share schemes\n\n#### Pricing is based on the level of support and number of scheme members. Minimum term is 12 months.\n\n#### **Choose annual billing to get two months free**.\n\nBilled annually\n\nBilled monthly\n\n#### Full Service\n\nThe works: hands-free equity management\n\n[Book a call](https://www.vestd.com/book-a-call-s0)\n\nEnquire for pricing\n\nEnquire for pricing\n\n Share scheme design, implementation & management\n\n Complete support and a dedicated account manager\n\n Briefing for your team\n\n Live HMRC submission support (via screen sharing, videos or phone)\n\n##### Most Popular\n\n#### Guided\n\nAll share schemes & guided support\n\n[Book a call](https://www.vestd.com/book-a-call-s0)\n\nFrom £4,200 / year\n\nFrom £420 / month\n\n Scheme set up support\n\n Unlimited valuations\n\n New share classes\n\n CSOP & phantom shares\n\n Live HMRC submission support (via screen sharing, videos or phone)\n\n#### Self-Serve\n\nSelf-service equity for small businesses\n\n[Book a call](https://www.vestd.com/book-a-call-s0)\n\nFrom £2,200 / year\n\nFrom £220 / month\n\n Only available to existing customers\n\n Share schemes for up to five recipients\n\n EMI Schemes, Growth Shares & Unapproved Options\n\nFull Companies House integration is included in all plans.\n\nReady to explore further?\n\n[Talk to a specialist](https://www.vestd.com/book-a-call-s0)\n\n## Share scheme management\n\n#### Build and motivate your team\n\n ### Tax-efficient rewards\n\nEasily set up and manage employee share schemes and digitise existing schemes. Vestd helps you design, issue, and track equity, making it simple to reward and motivate your team.\n\n[Get a demo](/book-a-call-s0)\n\n![pricing-rewards](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/pricing-rewards.png?width=1080&height=700&name=pricing-rewards.png)\n\n## Company secretarial\n\n#### File docs and forms at the touch of a button\n\n![pricing-investment-docs](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/pricing-investment-docs.png?width=1080&height=700&name=pricing-investment-docs.png)\n\n ### Wave goodbye to paperwork\n\nStay compliant and manage admin and legal tasks effortlessly. Vestd simplifies your statutory filing, shareholder communications, and record-keeping. Including automated filings and notifications.\n\n[Find out more](/companies-house)\n\n## Equity management\n\n#### Fully synced to Companies House for accuracy and speed\n\n ### A single source of truth\n\nKeep your cap table updated, issue shares, and hold your legal register all in one place. 100% digital: no forms to complete.\n\n[Find out more](/equity-management-software)\n\n![pricing-equity-management](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/pricing-equity-management.png?width=1080&height=700&name=pricing-equity-management.png)\n\n## Shareholder dashboards\n\n#### Get real-time updates and model future value scenarios\n\n![pricing-shareholder-dashboard](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/pricing-shareholder-dashboard.png?width=1080&height=700&name=pricing-shareholder-dashboard.png)\n\n ### Keep eyes on the prize\n\nShareholders can log in to track the value of their stake, calculate the potential value based on projected valuations, and receive real-time updates on any changes to their holdings.\n\n[Find out more](/shareholder-dashboards)\n\n> The platform itself allows you to manage all aspects of share and option management concisely in one place. The automations and integrations save you time. But while the platform is great, it is the team that makes Vestd stand out. From pre-sales to onboarding and the ever-helpful support team - not only do they support on the platform but provide excellent knowledge in this area.\n\n![Jenny James](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/Jenny%20J.webp)\n\nJenny James\n\nChief Operating Officer, Findr\n\n> Great platform. The team always provide brilliant support. I would definitely recommend using Vestd to anyone who needs to set up and administer an EMI scheme.\n\n![Sarah T.](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/reviews-sarah-t.webp)\n\nSarah T.\n\nDirector\n\n> Straight forward and structured approach - so good for founders and also FD/CFO/advisor who is looking to get share capital and share option schemes in place.\n\n![Ciaran O.](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/reviews-ciaran-o.webp)\n\nCiaran O.\n\nFounder\n\n> A fantastic platform. The price is fixed. The customer support is fantastic and readily available. They have held our hand right through the whole process.\n\n![Tim S.](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/reviews-tim-s.webp)\n\nTim S.\n\nInvestor\n\n> I love Vestd and I wish I had found it sooner. It makes the whole process of issuing shares whether they're growth shares or ordinary shares incredibly simple.\n\n![James B.](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/reviews-james-b.webp)\n\nJames B.\n\nCo-Founder\n\n> Amazing shift from Excel to Vestd. The support team were amazing and did a great job of completing our setup and we have been very pleased at being able to better manage our governance over time.\n\n![Dan W.](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/reviews-dan-w.webp)\n\nDan W.\n\nCo-Founder & CEO\n\n### Frequently asked questions\n\n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    What happens if I cancel my subscription?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    If you cancel your subscription, you'll lose access to all share scheme management features.\n    \n    This includes the ability to issue shares, reward employees, and manage what happens to a recipient’s options/shares when they leave the company.\n    \n    Your recipients will not be notified of their options vesting, you won’t be able to manage existing live shares, and you will have to manually track your option pool.  \n      \n    Additionally, you'll stop receiving the documents required for your HMRC notifications and lose access to document signing and storage features.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    Will I need to pay for your service yearly?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    Yes, our service comes with a minimum 12-month term, which automatically renews.\n    \n    We’ll send you a reminder before renewal, and our team is always available to ensure your plan continues to suit your needs.\n    \n    Our platform is designed to streamline the ongoing management of your scheme, giving you peace of mind each year.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    I only have two people in my scheme. Do I still pay the same rate?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    Our pricing is based on tiers, starting with plans for up to 10 recipients. You'll only pay for the number of recipients you need.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    Can I pay monthly and leave the platform after setup?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    No, our service requires a minimum 12-month commitment. The platform is built to offer ongoing support for managing your share scheme, including help with administration, document signing and storage, as well as automatic HMRC reminders, and more.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    Do your prices include VAT?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    VAT is charged in addition. \n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    What should I expect when I join?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    Once you sign up, depending on your pricing plan, your Customer Success contact will arrange a welcome call to guide you through the next steps.\n    \n    We’ll move at your pace, but your active involvement will be essential to ensure everything progresses smoothly.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    Can I change my plan?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    Yes, we understand your needs may evolve. After your initial 12-month term, we’ll gladly review your support and functionality requirements with you.\n    \n    You can also upgrade your plan at any time, which will start a new 12-month term.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    Is there a limit to the number of shareholders I can have?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    No, our platform allows you to manage an unlimited number of shareholders, unlike some other providers that may have restrictions.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    How many recipients can I include in my share scheme?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    Our pricing is tiered based on the number of recipients. To find the plan that best fits your needs, please speak with one of our Equity Consultants for personalised advice.\n    \n-   [\n    \n    #### \n    \n    How long is the subscription term?\n    \n    \n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    The minimum subscription term for all plans is 12 months.\n    \n    Subscriptions automatically renew each year, and we'll send you a reminder before the renewal date.\n    \n    If you need to cancel, you may do so after the initial 12-month period. However, we're always here to discuss any changes and make sure you're on the plan that best meets your needs.\n    \n\n### Compare plans\n\n-   Guided\n-   Self-Serve\n-   Essentials\n\nGuided\n\nSelf-Serve\n\nEssentials\n\nEquity management\n\nTwo-way Companies House integration\n\nWe automatically file documents with Companies House when required We’re also the only platform that pulls data from Companies House, which saves time when joining. [Learn more](https://www.vestd.com/companies-house).\n\nArticles of Association\n\nArticles of Association govern a company's internal affairs and management. We offer articles support with Companies House filings, and you can adopt the Vestd Articles for the ability to issue growth shares. [Learn more](https://www.vestd.com/help/a-brief-overview-of-vestd-articles-of-association).\n\nIssue shares\n\nIssue shares directly to new and existing shareholders and Vestd will take care of Companies House filings and generate share certificates for you to issue.\n\nShare certificates (branded)\n\nAll share issuances come with a share certificate for the shareholder. You can even customise them with your branding.\n\nShare authorisations\n\nAutomatically send the required resolutions to directors and shareholders to gain the authorisation to issue shares, options and growth shares.\n\nDigital cap table\n\nWhenever any share capital activity takes place on Vestd, your digital cap table will be automatically updated accordingly. You can also simulate different views and download the data for investors.\n\nSecure data room\n\nUpload documents, financial reports and investor prospectus to share with key stakeholders. Only those invited to each room will have access.\n\nUp to three\n\nScenario modelling\n\nUse our modelling tools and calculators to see how your share capital will look after investment rounds, option grants and other scenarios. In some cases this will require a share movement History upload process in order to model future value.\n\nShareholder dashboards\n\nAll shareholders and option holders invited to Vestd get their own dashboard where they can project the current and future value of their equity. Handy tax calculators show their potential profit too.\n\nUnlimited\n\nUp to 100\n\nUp to 25\n\nBusiness & legal documents\n\nWe provide complimentary document templates such as Advance Subscription Agreements, NDAs and Shareholders’ Agreements to help you streamline business procedures.\n\nCompany secretarial tools\n\nAll resolutions, confirmation statements and other company governance documents are stored on Vestd and sent to Companies House when required, making Co-Sec tasks much easier and virtually paperwork free.\n\nShareholder register\n\nVestd can be used as your legal shareholder register, granted all shareholders’ addresses are added and all share movement history is uploaded. Please note that only transactions made since joining the platform will have accurate dates. A share movement history upload may be required in some cases.\n\nConfirmation Statements\n\nConfirmation statements need to be submitted to Companies House each year. Vestd does pretty much all of it for you – we even pay the filing fee!\n\nDigital signing\n\nAll resolutions and other documents generated by the platform can be digitally signed via DocuSign. No printing, no faff. You can also upload your own documents for signing (up to the monthly limit).\n\nUp to 100 per month\n\nUp to 30 per month\n\nUp to 5 per month\n\nSubdivide existing shares\n\nSubdivisions (or share splits) create more shares in the company without diluting existing shareholders, making your share capital easier to distribute. Our subdivision tool basically does it all for you, answer a few questions and you’re done.\n\nBoard and shareholder resolutions\n\nWhen board/shareholder authorisation is needed, Vestd automatically generates the resolution and sends it to the appropriate people to sign, then files it with Companies House. You can also create bespoke resolutions for other business matters.\n\nAdd & change director details\n\nAny changes to your company’s directors are automatically filed with Companies House.\n\nChange the company name\n\nCompany name changes are automatically filed with Companies House.\n\nUpdate PSCs\n\nStock transfers\n\nA stock transfer is used to manage the sale or gifting of shares between shareholders. Vestd generates the Share Purchase Agreement and Stock Transfer Form for the relevant people to sign, then updates Companies House.\n\nShare buybacks\n\nCompanies can buy back shares from shareholders via Vestd, and we’ll update Companies House with the required paperwork and let you know whether Stamp Duty is due.\n\nNew share classes\n\nYou can create additional share classes for investment rounds or share schemes. Vestd takes out all the guesswork and files the required documents with Companies House.\n\nFrom £250\n\nFrom £250\n\nShare schemes\n\nCompany valuations (per year)\n\nOur in-house Valuation team provides valuations to ensure maximum tax certainty for your option holders.\n\nUnlimited\n\nShare scheme design\n\nAnswer a few simple questions in guided workflow and create a bespoke share scheme that aligns with your company’s goals.\n\nShare scheme legal docs\n\nYou can use Vestd’s agreements for your option and growth share schemes. Each agreement is customised to the unique needs and goals of each share scheme.\n\nGuided scheme design\n\nOur Customer Success team can help you design a share scheme based on your company’s goals.\n\nHMRC notification support\n\nWe’ll help you file the notifications to HMRC to keep your share schemes compliant.\n\nConditional equity\n\nSet time or performance-based conditions people must meet to earn their equity.\n\nFor up to 5 recipients\n\nCo-founder vesting\n\nCo-founder vesting schedules reward people for what they deliver while protecting them when someone fails to deliver.\n\nCo-founder prenups\n\nAlso known as an [Agile Partnership](https://www.vestd.com/agile-partnerships/). It aligns founders with key targets they must meet to earn their equity and ensures everyone’s best interests are protected.\n\nInitial equity consultation\n\nDiscuss your business goals with our Equity Consultants and they’ll recommend the best conditions to add to your share schemes to achieve them.\n\nSecond equity consultation\n\nA deeper dive into your company and its share capital.\n\nScheme types\n\nEnterprise Management Incentives (EMI)\n\nThe most popular and tax advantageous share scheme for UK businesses. [Learn more](https://www.vestd.com/emi-scheme).\n\nGrowth shares\n\nThe flexible way to reward virtually anyone for their help in growing your business. [Learn more](https://www.vestd.com/growth-shares).\n\nUnapproved options\n\nThe flexible way to grant options to virtually anyone. Set time or performance-based conditions recipients must meet for their options to vest. [Learn more](https://www.vestd.com/unapproved-share-options).\n\nAgile Partnerships\n\nCo-founder equity splits and prenups to protect the interests of founders and their business.\n\nOrdinary shares\n\nYou can easily issue shares to new and existing shareholders, with all the paperwork taken care of.\n\nCSOP\n\nCompany Share Option Plans are a tax efficient way to motivate, retain and reward employees.\n\nPhantom shares\n\nPhantom shares are a form of conditional equity, but instead of shares being issued upfront, the recipient receives a cash bonus equal to the value of the shares.\n\nOptions over shareholder shares\n\nGranting options over a shareholders’ shares avoids dilution. The process is usually complex, but incredibly simple with Vestd.\n\nCustomer support level\n\nSelf serve\n\nEmail\n\nScheduled video & phone support\n\nScheme design & management support\n\nAdd ons\n\nCompany incorporation\n\nOur guided workflow lets you incorporate a new company, create ordinary share classes, add directors and shareholders, and split the share capital. We’ll then send everything to Companies House.\n\n+£100\n\n+£100\n\n+£100\n\nInVestd Raise (fixed fee fundraising, S/EIS advance assurance)\n\nLaunch and execute funding rounds for just £150 / month. There are no other upfront or completion fees. Includes a funding consultation, S/EIS Advance Assurance, legal docs, data rooms, a pitch deck template, share issuance, and much more.\n\n£150 / mo\n\n£150 / mo\n\n£150 / mo\n\nAdditional valuations\n\nA company valuation is needed when granting shares/options and is typically valid for up to 90 days. If you use up your valuations for the year, you can get another for a one-off fee.\n\nFrom £1,000\n\nFrom £1,000\n\n409A valuations\n\nA type of valuation that’s essential when granting options to US taxpayers. This fee can be split into monthly payments.\n\nFrom £700\n\nFrom £700\n\nFrom £700\n\nExisting scheme digitisation\n\nUpload existing share schemes to Vestd for a one-off fee and eliminate paperwork and HMRC filing headaches. All shareholders and option holders invited to Vestd will get their own dashboard too. [Learn more](https://www.vestd.com/help/digitising-existing-schemes-with-vestd).\n\nFrom £250\n\nFrom £250\n\nLive HMRC submission support\n\nWe know how confusing and nervous it can be submitting things to HMRC. So our experts can guide you through the entire process over video call.\n\n+£25 / mo\n\nNew share classes\n\nYou can create additional share classes for investment rounds or share schemes. Vestd takes out all the guesswork and files the required documents with Companies House.\n\nFrom £250\n\nFrom £250\n\nCompanies House reconciliations\n\nWe’ll provide solutions for incorrect filings and other Companies House discrepancies so your Vestd account and cap table is all correct.\n\nFrom £25 / mo\n\nFrom £25 / mo\n\nBespoke option agreement digitisation\n\nIf you want to use your own option agreement template rather than Vestd’s option agreement, we can upload it to the platform ready for you to use.\n\nFrom £25 / mo\n\nVestd Nominee Structure for up to 50 shareholders\n\nFrom £50 / mo\n\nFrom £50 / mo\n\nFrom £50 / mo\n\nShare movement history\n\nRelevant if any activity has taken place since incorporation and before joining the platform. Our team will send you a data capture file for completion. Once received we will import your full cap table history into the platform. This will enable the share register and scenario modelling features to function fully.\n\nFrom £250\n\nFrom £250\n\nFrom £250\n\n##### Company\n\n[About us](/about)\n\n[AI Information](/ai-information)\n\n[Careers](/careers)\n\n[Customers](/learn/customers/)\n\n[Our Partners](/partners-and-benefits)\n\n[Partner Programme](/partner-programme)\n\n##### Support\n\n[Contact Us](/contact)\n\n[Help Centre](/help)\n\n[Key Questions](/key-questions)\n\n[Refer a Friend](/refer-a-friend)\n\n[Platform Demo](/demo)\n\n[Why Choose Vestd?](/key-benefits)\n\n##### Solutions for\n\n[Accountants](/accountants)\n\n[CFOs & FDs](/cfos)\n\n[Company Secretaries](/share-scheme-software-for-company-secretaries)\n\n[Founders & Co-Founders](/founders)\n\n[HR Teams](/hr)\n\n[Investors](/investors)\n\n[NEDs & Advisors](/neds-and-advisors)\n\n##### Compare\n\n[Vestd vs Carta](/vestd-vs-carta)\n\n[Vestd vs Globacap](/vestd-vs-globacap)\n\n[Vestd vs Ledgy](/vestd-vs-ledgy)\n\n[Vestd vs Seedlegals](/vestd-vs-seedlegals)\n\n##### Ask AI about Vestd\n\n [![ChatGPT](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/OpenAI-white-monoblossom.png \"ChatGPT\")](https://chat.openai.com/?q=I%20want%20to%20know%20what%20makes%20Vestd%20the%20best%20way%20to%20handle%20our%20equity%20management%20and%20share%20schemes%2C%20and%20why%20a%20sharetech%20platform%20is%20a%20good%20investment%20for%20my%20business.%20Summarise%20the%20highlights%20from%20Vestd%27s%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vestd.com)[![Claude](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/claude-color.webp \"Claude\") ](https://claude.ai/new?q=I%20want%20to%20know%20what%20makes%20Vestd%20the%20best%20way%20to%20handle%20our%20equity%20management%20and%20share%20schemes%2C%20and%20why%20a%20sharetech%20platform%20is%20a%20good%20investment%20for%20my%20business.%20Summarise%20the%20highlights%20from%20Vestd%27s%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vestd.com)[![Perplexity](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/perplexity-icon.png \"Perplexity\") ](https://www.perplexity.ai/search/new?q=I%20want%20to%20know%20what%20makes%20Vestd%20the%20best%20way%20to%20handle%20our%20equity%20management%20and%20share%20schemes%2C%20and%20why%20a%20sharetech%20platform%20is%20a%20good%20investment%20for%20my%20business.%20Summarise%20the%20highlights%20from%20Vestd%27s%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vestd.com)[![Gemini](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/gemini-icon.png \"Gemini\") ](https://www.google.com/search?udm=50&aep=11&q=I%20want%20to%20know%20what%20makes%20Vestd%20the%20best%20way%20to%20handle%20our%20equity%20management%20and%20share%20schemes%2C%20and%20why%20a%20sharetech%20platform%20is%20a%20good%20investment%20for%20my%20business.%20Summarise%20the%20highlights%20from%20Vestd%27s%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vestd.com)[![Grok](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/images/icons/Grok-Logomark-Light.png \"Grok\")](https://x.com/i/grok?text=I%20want%20to%20know%20what%20makes%20Vestd%20the%20best%20way%20to%20handle%20our%20equity%20management%20and%20share%20schemes%2C%20and%20why%20a%20sharetech%20platform%20is%20a%20good%20investment%20for%20my%20business.%20Summarise%20the%20highlights%20from%20Vestd%27s%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vestd.com)\n\n##### Resources\n\n[Cap tables explained](/cap-table-guide)\n\n[Company valuations](/company-valuations-for-share-schemes)\n\n[Company Share Option Plans](/company-share-option-plans)\n\n[Dividends](/dividends-explained)\n\n[EIS explained](/the-enterprise-investment-scheme)\n\n[Employee benefit ideas](/employee-benefits-list-for-uk-companies)\n\n[Employee Benefit Trusts](/employee-benefit-trusts)\n\n[Employee share schemes](/employee-share-schemes-guide)\n\n[Employee Stock Option Plans](/employee-stock-ownership-plans-guide)\n\n[Enterprise Management Incentives](/emi-share-options-scheme/)\n\n[Equity management](/equity-management-guide)\n\n[Growth shares explained](/growth-shares-explained)\n\n[How to set up a limited company](/how-to-set-up-a-limited-company-guide)\n\n[Ordinary shares](/what-are-ordinary-shares)\n\n[PISCES trading](/pisces/what-is-pisces)\n\n[Secondary markets explained](/secondary-markets-guide)\n\n[SEIS explained](/the-seed-enterprise-investment-scheme)\n\n[Special Purpose Vehicles (SPVs)](/special-purpose-vehicles-guide)\n\n[Unapproved share options](/unapproved-share-options-explained)\n\n[What is vesting?](/vesting-guide)\n\n[What are share options?](/share-options)\n\n![B-Corp-Logo-White-RGB](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/B-Corp-Logo-White-RGB.png?width=120&height=202&name=B-Corp-Logo-White-RGB.png)\n\n![ISO-27001 white logo](https://www.vestd.com/hs-fs/hubfs/ISO-27001%20white%20logo.png?width=140&height=135&name=ISO-27001%20white%20logo.png)\n\n**Vestd is directly authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority**\n\n[![vestd-logo-light](https://www.vestd.com/hubfs/vestd-logo-light.svg)](https://www.vestd.com)\n\n-   [Privacy Policy](https://app.vestd.com/privacy-policy/)\n-   [Use of cookies](https://www.vestd.com/cookies)\n\n© 2026 Vestd Ltd. Registered in England & Wales. Company Number 09302265.  \nVestd Services Limited Registered in England & Wales. Company Number 12625826.  \nRegistered office: Suite LU.231, The Light Bulb, 1 Filament Walk, Wandsworth, SW18 4GQ.  \nVestd Ltd is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority FRN 685992.\n\n[X](https://twitter.com/VestdHQ) [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/vestdhq/) [Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/company/vestd) [YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/@VestdHQ) [Tiktok](https://www.tiktok.com/@vestd)\n\n[Return to top](javascript:)",
