      "output": "  Start Your Company | SeedLegals     \n\n[![SeedLegals Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/seedlegals-logo.svg)](/)\n\n#### Startups made easy. Sorted.\n\n-   [\n    \n    For Founders\n    \n    ](#)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/start-icon.svg)\n    \n    Start\n    \n    Hire your team and get investment ready\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/start/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Essential Startup Contracts\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/legal-documents/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Founder Agreements\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Register a company\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/start/register-a-company/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Team Agreements\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Apply for SEIS & EIS\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/start/seis-eis/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Cap Table\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/start/cap-table/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Staff Handbook\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/staff-handbook/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Company Policies\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/company-policies/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Partner Perks\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/marketplace/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/raise-icon.svg)\n    \n    Raise\n    \n    Take care of everything you need to close investment.\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Pitch to Investors\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/pitch/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    SeedLegals Boost\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/boost/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Raise Before a Round\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-before-a-round/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Do a Funding Round\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-a-round/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Finance for Fundraising\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/resources/finance-for-fundraising/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Legal Advice for a Round\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Instant Investment\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/top-up-a-round/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    SEIS/EIS Compliance\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/seis-eis-compliance/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Data Room\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/data-room/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Rollup\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/raise/rollup/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/grow-icon.svg)\n    \n    Grow\n    \n    Manage shareholders and reward your team with equity.\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Share Option Schemes\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    EMI Option Schemes\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-option-schemes/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    EMI Valuation\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-valuation/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Unapproved Option Schemes\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/unapproved/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    R&D Tax Credits\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/rd-tax-credit-claim/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Legal Advisory Service\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/general-counsel/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Share Transfers\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-transfers/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Manage your board\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/board-management/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    USA Expansion\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/usa-expansion/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Delaware Flip\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/delaware-flip/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Flip & Raise\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/grow/flip-raise/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Sell your company\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.co