    Catch up on webinars and learn from specialists\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/videos/)\n    \n    Community\n    \n    [\n    \n    Events\n    \n    ](/events/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Newsletter\n    \n    ](/newsletters/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    Case Studies\n    \n    ](/customers/)\n    \n    Support\n    \n    [Help Centre](https://help.seedlegals.com/en)\n    \n    [Speak to our experts](/talk-to-an-expert/)\n    \n    [SeedLegals Academy](https://seedlegals.com/seedlegals-academy/)\n    \n    [\n    \n    ![Pitch Deck Template Download PRebiew image](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Pitch-deck-template-download.png)\n    \n    Nail your pitch and impress investors\n    \n    Get the pitch deck that’s helping 3,500+ founders raise. 12 customisable slides, plus insider tips from investors.\n    \n    Get the pitch deck\n    \n    \n    \n    ](/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n    \n-   [\n    \n    Company\n    \n    ](#)\n    -   [\n        \n        ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/about.svg)\n        \n        ##### About us\n        \n        SeedLegals is the one-stop platform for the legals you need to get funded and grow your business.\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/about/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Mission & values\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/about/mission-values/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Careers\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/careers/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Partners\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/partners-community/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Contact\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/contact/)\n    -   [\n        \n        ##### Media\n        \n        ](https://seedlegals.com/media/)\n\n[Start Free](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\nAlready have an account? [Log in](https://app.seedlegals.com/login)\n\n[](https://www.facebook.com/seedlegals)[](https://twitter.com/seedlegals)[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/15088107/)[](https://www.instagram.com/seedlegals/)\n\n![1 (4)](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/1-4.webp)\n\nGet SEIS/EIS ready. [**Download our free guide to an HMRC-friendly pitch deck**](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/seis-eis-pitch-deck-guide/).\n\n[Download now](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/seis-eis-pitch-deck-guide/)\n\n[](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/seis-eis-pitch-deck-guide/)\n\n![Group 2609265](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Group-2609265.webp)\n\nPitch Perfect: **[Get the pitch deck template investors want you to use.](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)**\n\n[Download now](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n\n[](https://seedlegals.com/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n\n![Tips From Investors Ebook](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/Tips-from-investors-eBook.webp)\n\nGet investment-ready! [**Get our best tips from active investors.**](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/tips-from-investors/)\n\n[Download now](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/tips-from-investors/)\n\n[](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/tips-from-investors/)\n\n[![SeedLegals Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/seedlegals-logo.svg)](/)\n\nFor Founders\n\n[\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/start-icon.svg)\n\nStart\n\nHire your team and get investment ready\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/)\n\n[\n\nEssential Startup Contracts\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/legal-documents/)\n\n[\n\nFounder Agreements\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)\n\n[\n\nRegister a company\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/register-a-company/)\n\n[\n\nTeam Agreements\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/)\n\n[\n\nApply for SEIS & EIS\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/seis-eis/)\n\n[\n\nCap Table\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/cap-table/)\n\n[\n\nStaff Handbook\n\n](https://seed