edlegals.com/meetings/investor-newsletter/)\n\n[\n\nMeet the team\n\nSee how SeedLegals helps streamline your investments\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/meetings/investor-interest/)\n\n[\n\n![Navigation Ad Book A Call Investor](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Navigation-ad_Book-a-call_Investor.jpg)\n\nGet deals done faster\n\nExplore our all-in-one platform: seamless deal flow, simplified investments, portfolio management and legal support.\n\nBook a demo\n\n\n\n](/meetings/investor-interest/)\n\n[\n\nPricing\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/pricing/)\n\n[\n\nResources\n\n\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/)\n\nInsights\n\n[\n\nArticles\n\nMust-have insights from industry experts, founders and investors\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/)[\n\nReports\n\nExpert analysis on trends we see from our data\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/reports/)[\n\nTermometer\n\nThe UK's most detailed analysis of early-stage funding deal terms\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/termometer/)\n\nCategories:\n\n[— SEIS/EIS](/resources/category/seis-eis/)\n\n[— Funding](/resources/category/funding-guides/)\n\n[— Options](/resources/category/share-option-schemes/)\n\n[— R&D](/resources/category/r-and-d-tax-credits/)\n\n[— Deal Data](/resources/category/deal-data/)\n\n[— News](/resources/category/news/)\n\n[— Investor Hub](/resources/category/investor-directory/)\n\nGuides\n\n[\n\nEbooks\n\nGet the ultimate startup starter kit\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/)[\n\nChecklists\n\nAce the admin with step-by-step guidance\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/checklists/)[\n\nVideos\n\nNEW\n\nCatch up on webinars and learn from specialists\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/videos/)\n\nCommunity\n\n[\n\nEvents\n\n](/events/)\n\n[\n\nNewsletter\n\n](/newsletters/)\n\n[\n\nCase Studies\n\n](/customers/)\n\nSupport\n\n[Help Centre](https://help.seedlegals.com/en)\n\n[Speak to our experts](/talk-to-an-expert/)\n\n[SeedLegals Academy](https://seedlegals.com/seedlegals-academy/)\n\n[\n\n![Pitch Deck Template Download PRebiew image](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/Pitch-deck-template-download.png)\n\nNail your pitch and impress investors\n\nGet the pitch deck that’s helping 3,500+ founders raise. 12 customisable slides, plus insider tips from investors.\n\nGet the pitch deck\n\n\n\n](/resources/pitch-deck-template-uk-startups/)\n\nCompany\n\n-   [\n    \n    ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/about.svg)\n    \n    About us\n    \n    SeedLegals is the one-stop platform for the legals you need to get funded and grow your business.\n    \n    ](https://seedlegals.com/about/)\n-   [Mission & values](https://seedlegals.com/about/mission-values/)\n-   [Careers](https://seedlegals.com/careers/)\n-   [Partners](https://seedlegals.com/partners-community/)\n-   [Contact](https://seedlegals.com/contact/)\n-   [Media](https://seedlegals.com/media/)\n\n![en](/wp-content/uploads/flags/en.png)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/lang-selector-chev.svg)\n\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/fr.png)FR](https://seedlegals.com/fr/creation-startup/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/us.png)US](https://seedlegals.com/us/start/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/ie.png)IE](https://seedlegals.com/ie/start/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/hk.png)HK](https://seedlegals.com/hk/start/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/sg.png)SG](https://seedlegals.com/sg/start/?nr=1)\n\n[+44 20 4587 5701](tel:+442045875701)\n\n[Login](https://app.seedlegals.com/login)\n\n[Start Free](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n-   [Start](https://seedlegals.com/start/)\n-   [Raise](https://seedlegals.com/raise/)\n-   [Grow](https://seedlegals.com/grow/)\n\n[Founder Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)\n\n# Start your company right\n\nEasily create the exact legals you need to hire, reward your team and get ready for your first investment.\n\n[\n\nStart Free\n\n](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)[\n\nSign up with Google\n\n](https://app.seedlegals.com/signup)\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Start-scaled.png)\n\n![Founders Background](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/founders-bg.svg)\n\n![Oddbox Cover Photo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/OddBox-Cover-Photo-e1572526923823.jpeg)\n\n![SeedLegal's Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/sl-logo.svg)\n\n###### Founder’s Journey\n\n### “More than just legal docs! SeedLegals educates founders on fundraising and democratises the process for everybody. ”\n\n  \n\n##### OddBox\n\nCo-Founder, Emilie Vanpoperinghe\n\n![Oddbox Transparent](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/OddBox-transparent-300x114.png)\n\n![Shape](/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/shapes/circle.svg)\n\n###### Founder Agreements\n\n## Create your founder agreements\n\nCreate airtight agreements that protect you, your company and co-founders in case things go wrong - which happens more than you'd think!\n\n[Learn more](/start/founder-agreements/)\n\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Salary & equity\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Share Vesting\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)IP assignment\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Founder-Agreement-alt.png)\n\n###### Team Agreements\n\n## Hire & reward your team\n\nOur customisable hiring agreements make that super easy. Set work hours, roles, reporting, probation, termination, assign bonus, stock options and more.\n\n[Learn more](/start/team-agreements/)\n\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Employment Agreements\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Advisors & NEDs Agreements\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Contractor Agreements\n-   ![tick](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/tick.svg)Intern Hiring Agreement\n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Team-Agreements.png)\n\n###### Advance Assurance\n\n## Get SEIS & EIS Approved\n\nAdvance Assurance makes you dramatically more investable. Do your Advance Assurance with SeedLegals and get approved faster than anywhere else.\n\n[Get Started](/start/seis-eis/)\n\n![SVG](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/seis-2.svg)\n\n# 98%\n\nsuccess rate through SeedLegals vs. industry standard of 62%.\n\n![Shape](/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/shapes/circle.svg)\n\n###### Cap Table\n\n## Keep tabs on who owns what\n\nForget managing your equity in Excel. There’s an insanely better way. Build your cap table on SeedLegals and automatically keep tabs on who owns what.\n\n[Learn more](/start/cap-table-2/)\n\n-   ##### Say goodbye to cap table mistakes\n    \n    1 in 3 startup cap tables are broken. With SeedLegals your cap table is always up-to-date.\n    \n\n![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/Cap-Table-3.png)\n\n## You’re in safe hands\n\nOur team of legal and funding experts have helped thousands of entrepreneurs raise money and grow their businesses.\n\n-   ##### Beautifully organised\n    \n    Your company's core agreements, all in one place\n    \n-   ##### Secure signatures\n    \n    Share and collect signatures online via SeedLegals\n    \n-   ##### Backed by real lawyers\n    \n    Create the exact documents you need at every stage of growth\n    \n-   ##### Serious about security\n    \n    Your information stays safe and confidential in our secure system\n    \n-   ##### Helpful humans\n    \n    Talk to one of our friendly team anytime on live chat\n    \n-   ##### Extra protection\n    \n    Don't worry, our insurance covers claims related to our platform\n    \n\n## We’ve helped over 60,000\n\ncompanies\n\nFrom food to FinTech and beyond, join thousands of startups who use SeedLegals to start, raise and grow faster.\n\n-   ![Yoller](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Yoller-e1574964551789.png)\n-   ![Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/logo.png)\n-   ![Pluto 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Pluto-2-e1573751477232.png)\n-   ![The Family 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/The-family-2.png)\n-   ![Trim It](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/trim-it-w-e1590253311428.png)\n-   ![Oddbox Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/oddbox-logo-e1573757173841.png)\n\n[More customer stories](/customers/)\n\n-   ![Louise Doherty](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Louise-Doherty.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    The reality is you’re on a journey; fundraising is so much about the narrative. SeedLegals allows you to tell the right story at the right time with the right legal documents for different types of investors.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Louise Doherty\n    \n    Founder & CEO, Yoller\n    \n    ![Yoller](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Yoller-e1574964551789.png)\n    \n-   ![Qure](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Qure-e1573739439847.png)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    SeedLegals held our hand through complex investor negotiations and even picked up on some errors produced by our previous lawyers which were a well-known City law firm!\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Alex Templeton\n    \n    Founder & CEO, Qured\n    \n    ![Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/logo.png)\n    \n-   ![Pluto](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/PLuto-e1573751551277.png)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    One of the great things about SeedLegals is that it is designed to be appropriate for the round and the stage of the business. They keep it simple. It feels like they really understand that.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Alex Rainey\n    \n    Co-founder & CEO, Pluto\n    \n    ![Pluto 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Pluto-2-600x600.png)\n    \n-   ![Thefamily](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/thefamily.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    How do I get all the businesses I invest in to use SeedLegals?\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Alexander Wyndham\n    \n    Angel Investor , The Family\n    \n    ![The Family 2](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/The-family-2.png)\n    \n-   ![Darren Trimit](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Darren-Trimit.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    It's easy to forget about the legal side of things but SeedLegals make things really easy to understand. The team at SeedLegals are truly amazing.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Darren Tenkorang\n    \n    Founder, TRIM-IT\n    \n    ![Trim It](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/trim-it-w-600x329.png)\n    \n-   ![](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Oddbox-founders.jpg)\n    \n    ![Quotes](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/quotes.svg)\n    \n    There’s an opportunity to reach a specialist advisor via chat, phone and email to check in on anything. The SeedLegals team were extremely responsive – really amazing.\n    \n      \n    \n    ##### Emilie Vanpoperinghe\n    \n    Co-Founder, OddBox\n    \n    ![Oddbox Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/oddbox-logo-600x229.png)\n    \n\n-   ![Yoller](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/Yoller-e1574964551789.png)\n-   ![Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/