 Logo](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/sl-logo-drop.svg)\n\n### Startups made easy. Sorted.\n\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/fr.png)FR](https://seedlegals.com/fr/creation-startup/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/us.png)US](https://seedlegals.com/us/start/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/ie.png)IE](https://seedlegals.com/ie/start/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/hk.png)HK](https://seedlegals.com/hk/start/?nr=1)\n-   [![](/wp-content/uploads/flags/sg.png)SG](https://seedlegals.com/sg/start/?nr=1)\n\n##### [Start\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/start/)\n\n[Essential Startup Contracts](https://seedlegals.com/legal-documents/)\n\n[Founder Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/founder-agreements/)\n\n[Register a company](https://seedlegals.com/start/register-a-company/)\n\n[Team Agreements](https://seedlegals.com/start/team-agreements/)\n\n[SEIS/EIS Advance Assurance](https://seedlegals.com/start/seis-eis/)\n\n[Cap Table](https://seedlegals.com/start/cap-table/)\n\n[Staff Handbook](https://seedlegals.com/staff-handbook/)\n\n[Company Policies](https://seedlegals.com/grow/company-policies/)\n\n[Partner Perks](https://seedlegals.com/marketplace/)\n\n##### [Raise\n\n](/raise/)\n\n[Pitch to Investors](https://seedlegals.com/raise/pitch/)\n\n[SeedLegals Boost](https://seedlegals.com/raise/boost/)\n\n[Raise Before a Round](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-before-a-round/)\n\n[Do a Funding Round](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-a-round/)\n\n[Do a Series A Round](https://seedlegals.com/raise/raise-series-a-round/)\n\n[Legal Advice for a Round](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/)\n\n[Instant Investment](https://seedlegals.com/raise/top-up-a-round/)\n\n[SEIS/EIS Compliance](https://seedlegals.com/raise/seis-eis-compliance/)\n\n[Data Room](https://seedlegals.com/raise/data-room/)\n\n[Finance for Fundraising](https://seedlegals.com/raise/finance-for-fundraising/)\n\n##### [Grow\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/grow/)\n\n[Share Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/)\n\n[EMI Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-option-schemes/)\n\n[EMI Valuation](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/emi-valuation/)\n\n[Unapproved Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-options-scheme/unapproved/)\n\n[R&D Tax Credits](https://seedlegals.com/grow/rd-tax-credit-claim/)\n\n[R&D Tax Credit Calculator](https://seedlegals.com/rd-calculator/)\n\n[Legal Advisory Service](https://seedlegals.com/advisory/general-counsel/)\n\n[Share Transfers](https://seedlegals.com/grow/share-transfers/)\n\n[Manage your board](https://seedlegals.com/board-management/)\n\n[USA Expansion](https://seedlegals.com/grow/usa-expansion/)\n\n[Delaware Flip](https://seedlegals.com/grow/delaware-flip/)\n\n[Flip & Raise](https://seedlegals.com/grow/flip-raise/)\n\n[Sell your company](https://seedlegals.com/grow/exit/)\n\n##### [Investors\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/investors/)\n\n[Create a syndicate](/investors/syndicate/)\n\n[Run your deal](/investors/deal-manager/)\n\n[Get SEIS/EIS relief](/investors/investor-seis/)\n\n[Manage your portfolio](/investors/exit-modelling/)\n\n##### Resources\n\n[Startup Guides](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/startup-guides/)\n\n[Funding Guides](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/funding-guides/)\n\n[SEIS EIS](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/seis-eis/)\n\n[Option Schemes](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/share-option-schemes/)\n\n[R&D Guides](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/r-and-d-tax-credits/)\n\n[Termometer](https://seedlegals.com/termometer/)\n\n[Deal Data](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/deal-data/)\n\n[Checklists](https://seedlegals.com/checklists/)\n\n[ebooks](https://seedlegals.com/ebooks/)\n\n[Newsletters](https://seedlegals.com/newsletters/)\n\n[Find Investors](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/investor-directory/)\n\n[Investor Hub](https://seedlegals.com/resources/category/investor-hub/)\n\n[Help Centre](https://help.seedlegals.com/en)\n\n[SeedLegals Academy](https://seedlegals.com/seedlegals-academy/)\n\n##### [About\n\n](https://seedlegals.com/about/)\n\n[Mission & values](https://seedlegals.com/about/mission-values/)\n\n[Partners Community](https://seedlegals.com/partners-community/)\n\n[Become a partner](https://seedlegals.com/partners/)\n\n[Our authors and experts](https://seedlegals.com/authors-and-experts/)\n\n[Case studies](https://seedlegals.com/customers/)\n\n[For Accountants](https://seedlegals.com/for-accountants/)\n\n[Events](https://seedlegals.com/events/)\n\n[Media](https://seedlegals.com/media/)\n\n© SeedLegals 2026. All Rights Reserved.\n\n[Privacy Policy](https://seedlegals.com/privacy-policy/) [Terms Of Service](https://seedlegals.com/terms-of-service/) [Cookie Policy](https://seedlegals.com/cookie-policy/) [Editorial Policy](https://seedlegals.com/editorial-policy/)\n\n [![facebook](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/facebook.svg)](https://www.facebook.com/seedlegals)[![twitter](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/x.svg) ](https://twitter.com/seedlegals)[![instagram](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/instagram.svg) ](https://www.instagram.com/seedlegals/)[![linkedin](https://seedlegals.com/wp-content/themes/theme/dist/images/social/footer/linkedin.svg)](https://www.linkedin.com/company/15088107/)",
