 easily.](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.policybee.co.uk%2Fit%2Dcontractor%2Dinsurance&rut=85a8a8910e0916599c3a0019dfd03a2686b962ce762657165814e75490ad107c)\n\n## [IT Contractors Professional Indemnity Insurance](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fcompareprofessionalindemnityinsurance.co.uk%2Fprofessional%2Findemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dit%2Dcontractors%2F&rut=ebd61271df97274cb2cc5ea40d56ac7678f42fa4cf0df74c3b62a789ab874254)\n\n [![](//external-content.duckduckgo.com/ip3/compareprofessionalindemnityinsurance.co.uk.ico)](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fcompareprofessionalindemnityinsurance.co.uk%2Fprofessional%2Findemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dit%2Dcontractors%2F&rut=ebd61271df97274cb2cc5ea40d56ac7678f42fa4cf0df74c3b62a789ab874254)[compareprofessionalindemnityinsurance.co.uk/professional/indemnity-insurance-it-contractors/](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fcompareprofessionalindemnityinsurance.co.uk%2Fprofessional%2Findemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dit%2Dcontractors%2F&rut=ebd61271df97274cb2cc5ea40d56ac7678f42fa4cf0df74c3b62a789ab874254)\n\n[What does **professional** **indemnity** insurance cover for it **contractors**? **Professional** **indemnity** insurance typically covers legal defence costs and compensation for claims alleging negligence, breach of **professional** duty and negligent misstatement.](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fcompareprofessionalindemnityinsurance.co.uk%2Fprofessional%2Findemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dit%2Dcontractors%2F&rut=ebd61271df97274cb2cc5ea40d56ac7678f42fa4cf0df74c3b62a789ab874254)\n\n## [Compare professional indemnity insurance quotes - MoneySuperMarket](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneysupermarket.com%2Fbusiness%2Dinsurance%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2F&rut=488ec235b46e0a56dda05a32099c81f66834f5f1b67e62c0dce2c55def5833e8)\n\n [![](//external-content.duckduckgo.com/ip3/www.moneysupermarket.com.ico)](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneysupermarket.com%2Fbusiness%2Dinsurance%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2