e24.](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insure24.co.uk%2Fit%2Dcontractor%2Dprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance%2F&rut=c230ef50e401bf07ba4d026f02a0edfefc7555ad307838251abd006995f1e472)\n\n## [Professional Indemnity Insurance Calculator UK 2026 — Cost Guide](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fukcalculator.com%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dcalculator.html&rut=9cfa67fa41acb3d0393facc2ab5878b1d190702aeb90bb724219f498fcb553f8)\n\n [![](//external-content.duckduckgo.com/ip3/ukcalculator.com.ico)](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fukcalculator.com%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dcalculator.html&rut=9cfa67fa41acb3d0393facc2ab5878b1d190702aeb90bb724219f498fcb553f8)[ukcalculator.com/professional-indemnity-insurance-calculator.html](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fukcalculator.com%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dcalculator.html&rut=9cfa67fa41acb3d0393facc2ab5878b1d190702aeb90bb724219f498fcb553f8)\n\n[**Professional** **Indemnity** Insurance Calculator Estimate your PI insurance cost, find the right level of cover for your profession, and understand regulatory requirements. Indicative **UK** market rates.](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fukcalculator.com%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance%2Dcalculator.html&rut=9cfa67fa41acb3d0393facc2ab5878b1d190702aeb90bb724219f498fcb553f8)\n\n## [Professional Indemnity Insurance - Compare Cheap Quotes](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quotezone.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2Dinsurance%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance&rut=067f3014fc8ff904324894efa8ca1512f1c1fab75c82a0c9dcef60f032f1cae4)\n\n [![](//external-content.duckduckgo.com/ip3/www.quotezone.co.uk.ico)](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quotezone.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2Dinsurance%2Fprofessional%2Dindemnity%2Dinsurance&rut=067f3014fc8ff904324894efa8ca1512f1c1fab75c82a0c9dcef60f032f1cae4)[www.quotezone.co.uk/business-insurance/professional-indemnity-insurance](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.quotezone.co.uk%