      "text": "The user wants to know all the places where they'd find the Common Paper standard contract templates (NDA, PSA, CSA, ToS, DPA, etc.) plus the broader category of free/cheap standard contract templates. Let me give them a comprehensive list of where these templates live — Common Paper's full catalog + similar free template libraries.\n\nLet me fetch the Common Paper standards page and the language library to give a completelist of what's there.",
