      "code": "{\"url\": \"https://commonpaper.com/standards/\", \"format\": \"markdown\"}",
      "output": "     Standard Contracts - Common Paper                                                                      \n\n[Skip to content](#content)\n\n## Main Navigation\n\n[](https://commonpaper.com/)\n\n-   [Standards](https://commonpaper.com/standards/ \"Standards\")\n-   [Product](# \"Product\")\n    -   [Contract management](https://commonpaper.com/product/ \"Contract management\")\n    -   [AI contract review](https://commonpaper.com/product/ai-agent/ \"AI contract review\")\n-   [Pricing](https://commonpaper.com/pricing/ \"Pricing\")\n-   [Committee](https://commonpaper.com/committee/ \"Committee\")\n-   [About](https://commonpaper.com/about/ \"About\")\n-   [Sign in](https://app.commonpaper.com/auth/auth0?screen_hint=signin \"Sign in\")\n-   [Sign up free](https://app.commonpaper.com/auth/auth0?screen_hint=signup \"Sign up free\")\n\n# Standard Contracts\n\nCommon Paper standard agreements have been downloaded more than 40,000 times and used to close millions of dollars in deals. They are created and maintained by a committee of expert attorneys and released for free under the Creative Commons CC BY 4.0 License.\n\nFind an agreement for... Find an agreement for...\n\n[Confidentiality](javascript:void\\(0\\);) [Design](javascript:void\\(0\\);) [Clickthrough terms](javascript:void\\(0\\);) [Sales and services](javascript:void\\(0\\);) [Partnerships](javascript:void\\(0\\);) [Compliance](javascript:void\\(0\\);) [All agreements](javascript:void\\(0\\);)\n\n[Mutual Non-Disclosure Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/mutual-nda/ \"Mutual Non-Disclosure Agreement\")\n\n## Mutual Non-Disclosure Agreement\n\nNDA Not sure? Start here\n\nConfidently share information with another party.\n\n[Terms of Service](https://commonpaper.com/standards/terms-of-service/ \"Terms of Service\")\n\n## Terms of Service\n\nTOS\n\nClickthrough terms for selling cloud services or SaaS.\n\n[Design Partner Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/design-partner-agreement/ \"Design Partner Agreement\")\n\n## Design Partner Agreement\n\nDesign\n\nCollaborate with your first users and customers as an early-stage startup.\n\n[Cloud Service Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/cloud-service-agreement/ \"Cloud Service Agreement\")\n\n## Cloud Service Agreement\n\nCSA\n\nSell cloud software and SaaS products.\n\n[Service Level Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/service-level-agreement/ \"Service Level Agreement\")\n\n## Service Level Agreement\n\nSLA\n\nSet cloud service performance targets.\n\n[Data Processing Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/data-processing-agreement/ \"Data Processing Agreement\")\n\n## Data Processing Agreement\n\nDPA\n\nEstablish how personal data will be processed.\n\n[Business Associate Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/business-associate-agreement/ \"Business Associate Agreement\")\n\n## Business Associate Agreement\n\nBAA\n\nEnsure safe keeping of Protected Health Information.\n\n[Professional Services Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/professional-services-agreement/ \"Professional Services Agreement\")\n\n## Professional Services Agreement\n\nPSA\n\nSell services and custom deliverables.\n\n[AI Addendum](https://commonpaper.com/standards/ai-addendum/ \"AI Addendum\")\n\n## AI Addendum\n\nAI\n\nCover AI-related data use, IP, and risk.\n\n[Partnership Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/partnership-agreement/ \"Partnership Agreement\")\n\n## Partnership Agreement\n\nPartner\n\nSet up referrals, sponsorships, and co-marketing relationships.\n\n[Software License Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/software-license-agreement/ \"Software License Agreement\")\n\n## Software License Agreement\n\nSoftware\n\nLicense on-prem or self-hosted software.\n\n[Pilot Agreement](https://commonpaper.com/standards/pilot-agreement/ \"Pilot Agreement\")\n\n## Pilot Agreement\n\npilot\n\nOffer a trial to evaluate fit before the sale.\n\n### Other documents and resources\n\n[Language Library](/language-library)\n\n## Language Library\n\nPre-written clauses you can add to make common modifications.\n\n[Letter of Intent](/documents/letter-of-intent)\n\n## Letter of Intent\n\nLOI\n\nSecure proof of interest from future customers.\n\n[One-way NDA](/documents/one-way-nda)\n\n## One-way NDA\n\nShare information securely.\n\n[Term Sheet](/documents/term-sheet)\n\n## Term Sheet\n\nOutline terms for strategic partnerships\n\n[Independent Contractor Agreement](/documents/independent-contractor-agreement)\n\n## Independent Contractor Agreement\n\nSet terms for freelance and consulting work.\n\n[Amendment](/documents/amendment)\n\n## Amendment\n\nUpdate any agreement.\n\n[Statement of Work](/documents/statement-of-work)\n\n## Statement of Work\n\nSOW\n\nDefine project scope and deliverables for Professional Services.\n\n[Order Form](/documents/order-form)\n\n## Order Form\n\nOrder form for Cloud Service Agreements\n\n---\n\n---\n\nWe don’t offer a agreement yet. You can [contact us](https://commonpaper.com/about#get-in-touch) and tell us more about your use case.\n\n## Built to make contracting better\n\nWe're taking a new approach to contracting, designed by experts.\n\n![Standards](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/image-standards-2.png)\n\n### The Common Paper Committee\n\nOur standard agreements are created by a committee of dozens of attorneys representing technology vendors, procurement teams, boutique firms, and Big Law.\n\n[Meet the Committee](/committee \"Common Paper Committee\")\n\n![Standards](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/image-standards-3.png)\n\n### A streamlined structure for commercial contracts\n\nCommon Paper agreements have two parts:\n\n#### **The Cover Page**\n\nContains the variables that allow you to customize an agreement to suit your specific needs. All negotiations happen in the Cover Page.\n\n#### **The Standard Terms**\n\nThe static structure that creates reliability. Standard Terms are identical for everyone.\n\n![Standards](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/image-standards-1.png)\n\n### Standards make contracting easier for everyone\n\nOur standard agreements are drafted to start each negotiation on fair and reasonable terms for both sides. Because the Standard Terms never change, both vendors and buyers can review them once and rely on them over and over.\n\n![Creative Commons logo](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/icon-cc.svg)\n\nCommon Paper agreements are free to use and modify under the  \n[Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License.](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)\n\n## Standard contracts get results\n\n40,000+ contract downloads\n\n63% of contracts signed within 24 hours\n\n47% reduction in counterparty paper\n\n> “I've seen acquisitions where there were landmines hidden in contracts, but I was relieved to find out that Turbine was on Common Paper. That eliminated a whole class of potential problems that could have thrown a wrench in the deal. Anything that checks items off the due diligence list faster is good for founders and for us.”\n> \n> Andrew MacLeod, General Counsel, **Settle** (acquired Turbine, a Common Paper user, in 2024)\n\n## Ready to get started?\n\n[Choose an agreement](#primary \"Common Paper Standard Agreements\")\n\n![Common Paper logo](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/common-paper-logomark.svg)\n\n[Company](/ \"Common Paper Home\")\n\n-   [Home](/ \"Home\")\n-   [About](/about \"About\")\n-   [Join the Team](mailto:team@commonpaper.com \"Email the team at: team@commonpaper.com\")\n\n[Agreements](/standards \"Common Paper Standard Agreements\")\n\n-   [All Standard Agreements](/standards \"Standards\")\n-   [SaaS Agreement Toolkit](/resources/saas-agreement-toolkit \"SaaS Agreement Toolkit\")\n-   [Mutual NDA](/standards/mutual-nda \"Standard Mutual NDA\")\n-   [Cloud Service Agreement](/standards/cloud-service-agreement \"Cloud Service Agreement\")\n-   [Committee](/committee \"Committee\")\n\n[Resources](/resources \"Common Paper Resources\")\n\n-   [Language Library](/language-library \"Language Library\")\n-   [Blog](/blog \"Blog\")\n-   [Help Center](https://help.commonpaper.com/en/ \"Help Center\")\n-   [Status](https://status.commonpaper.com/ \"System status\")\n-   [Support](/support \"Support\")\n\n[Product](/product \"Common Paper Product\")\n\n-   [Product Features](/product \"Product Features\")\n-   [AI Negotiation](/product/ai-agent \"AI negotation\")\n-   [Pricing](/pricing \"Pricing\")\n-   [Release Notes](/release-notes/ \"Release Notes\")\n-   [API Documentation](https://api.commonpaper.com/docs \"API Documentation\")\n\n-   [Sign up free](https://app.commonpaper.com/auth/auth0?screen_hint=signup \"Sign up free\")\n-   [Website Terms of Use](/website-terms-of-use \"Website Terms of Use\")\n-   [Privacy Policy](/privacy-policy \"Privacy Policy\")\n\nCommon Paper, Inc. is not a law firm and communications with the company are not confidential or protected by the attorney-client privilege. We cannot provide any kind of legal advice. Forms provided by Common Paper are not customized for any particular client and are not a substitute for a lawyer. See our [Disclaimer](/disclaimer \"Common Paper Disclaimer\") page for details about using our forms.\n\n2025 © Common Paper. All rights reserved.\n\n[](https://twitter.com/UseCommonPaper \"Common Paper on Twitter\")[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/common-paper \"Common Paper on LinkedIn\")",
