      "output": "     Let’s agree on what matters - Common Paper                                                                         \n\n[Skip to content](#content)\n\n## Main Navigation\n\n[](https://commonpaper.com/)\n\n-   [Standards](https://commonpaper.com/standards/ \"Standards\")\n-   [Product](# \"Product\")\n    -   [Contract management](https://commonpaper.com/product/ \"Contract management\")\n    -   [AI contract review](https://commonpaper.com/product/ai-agent/ \"AI contract review\")\n-   [Pricing](https://commonpaper.com/pricing/ \"Pricing\")\n-   [Committee](https://commonpaper.com/committee/ \"Committee\")\n-   [About](https://commonpaper.com/about/ \"About\")\n-   [Sign in](https://app.commonpaper.com/auth/auth0?screen_hint=signin \"Sign in\")\n-   [Sign up free](https://app.commonpaper.com/auth/auth0?screen_hint=signup \"Sign up free\")\n\n# Let’s agree on what matters\n\nBuying and selling technology is still harder than it should be, and there’s a painful roadblock keeping it this way: the negotiation and approval of contracts.\n\n[Our vision is that contracts should be APIs](https://commonpaper.com/blog/contracts-should-be-apis/) – programmatically accessible and built on open-source standards. To make that vision a reality, we’ve assembled an amazing team of technologists, operators, and legal minds.\n\nCommon Paper is backed by venture investors and angels including founders, operators, and attorneys from some of the most exciting companies in tech. We’re a growing, all-remote team located across the US.\n\n## We’re embarking on a big journey, but it isn’t our first\n\n### Jake Stein, CEO\n\nJake previously co-founded RJMetrics (acquired by Magento) and Stitch (acquired by Talend), where he experienced the pain of contract negotiation firsthand.\n\n### Benjamin Garvey, CTO\n\nBen has been building software and teams for over two decades as an engineering leader at Betterment, Adobe, Magento, and RJMetrics.\n\n### Our investors\n\n![Boldstart logo](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/investor-boldstart.jpeg)\n\n![Uncork Capital logo](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/investor-uncork.png)\n\n![Y Combinator logo](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/investor-yc.png)\n\n### Join us\n\nWe’re building a culture where employees feel empowered to show up as their genuine selves, every day. Common Paper is a remote-first company.\n\n[Email us](mailto:team@commonpaper.com \"Email: team@commonpaper.com\")\n\n## Get in touch\n\nSomething on your mind? Let us know.\n\nYour name \n\nYour email \n\nYour comment or question\n\n### Thank you for contacting us!\n\nWe appreciate you reaching out. We'll be in touch soon.\n\n![Common Paper logo](https://commonpaper.com/wp-content/themes/understrap/assets/common-paper-logomark.svg)\n\n[Company](/ \"Common Paper Home\")\n\n-   [Home](/ \"Home\")\n-   [About](/about \"About\")\n-   [Join the Team](mailto:team@commonpaper.com \"Email the team at: team@commonpaper.com\")\n\n[Agreements](/standards \"Common Paper Standard Agreements\")\n\n-   [All Standard Agreements](/standards \"Standards\")\n-   [SaaS Agreement Toolkit](/resources/saas-agreement-toolkit \"SaaS Agreement Toolkit\")\n-   [Mutual NDA](/standards/mutual-nda \"Standard Mutual NDA\")\n-   [Cloud Service Agreement](/standards/cloud-service-agreement \"Cloud Service Agreement\")\n-   [Committee](/committee \"Committee\")\n\n[Resources](/resources \"Common Paper Resources\")\n\n-   [Language Library](/language-library \"Language Library\")\n-   [Blog](/blog \"Blog\")\n-   [Help Center](https://help.commonpaper.com/en/ \"Help Center\")\n-   [Status](https://status.commonpaper.com/ \"System status\")\n-   [Support](/support \"Support\")\n\n[Product](/product \"Common Paper Product\")\n\n-   [Product Features](/product \"Product Features\")\n-   [AI Negotiation](/product/ai-agent \"AI negotation\")\n-   [Pricing](/pricing \"Pricing\")\n-   [Release Notes](/release-notes/ \"Release Notes\")\n-   [API Documentation](https://api.commonpaper.com/docs \"API Documentation\")\n\n-   [Sign up free](https://app.commonpaper.com/auth/auth0?screen_hint=signup \"Sign up free\")\n-   [Website Terms of Use](/website-terms-of-use \"Website Terms of Use\")\n-   [Privacy Policy](/privacy-policy \"Privacy Policy\")\n\nCommon Paper, Inc. is not a law firm and communications with the company are not confidential or protected by the attorney-client privilege. We cannot provide any kind of legal advice. Forms provided by Common Paper are not customized for any particular client and are not a substitute for a lawyer. See our [Disclaimer](/disclaimer \"Common Paper Disclaimer\") page for details about using our forms.\n\n2025 © Common Paper. All rights reserved.\n\n[](https://twitter.com/UseCommonPaper \"Common Paper on Twitter\")[](https://www.linkedin.com/company/common-paper \"Common Paper on LinkedIn\")",
