      "text": "Good — Common Paper is **YC-backed** (not just BigLaw), founded by Jake Stein (ex-RJMetrics, ex-Stitch) and Ben Garvey. That's a YC-backed Delaware C-corp. So `.com` is not a sign of incomplete — actually `.com` here means it IS the company.\n\nNow let me find the Welsh Government templates. Let me try differentURLs.",
