      "output": "Sell2Wales: Welcome to Sell2Wales - Sell2Wales     \n\n[Skip to main content](#content)\n\n  \n\n \n\n  \n\nWe've saved some files called cookies on your device. These cookies are:\n\n-   essential for the site to work\n-   to help improve our website by collecting and reporting information on how you use it\n\nWe would also like to save some cookies to help tailor communications.\n\n \n\nBETA\n\nYou're viewing an updated version of this service - your feedback will help us to improve it.\n\n[Give Feedback](mailto:help@sell2wales.gov.wales?subject=Sell2Wales Site Feedback)\n\n[](#mobileExtraFeedbackOptions)\n\n[Give Feedback](mailto:help@sell2wales.gov.wales?subject=Sell2Wales Site Feedback)\n\n[Scheduled Downtime - Saturday 27th June 2026](/PortalMessages/Portal_MessageView.aspx?id=558)\n\nUpdated 16 June 2026\n\n[Hide](javascript:__doPostBack\\('ctl00$ctrlMessageBar$rptSiteMessages$ctl00$lbDismissMessage',''\\))\n\n[![Welsh Government logo](/S2WWeb/Images/wg-white.svg)](https://gov.wales)\n\n[Cymraeg](/Redirect/GoAlt.aspx?redirectUrl=%2fdefault.aspx)\n\n[![Sell2Wales Logo](/S2WWeb/Images/s2w-en.png)](/)\n\n[Sign in](javascript:__doPostBack\\('ctl00$ctl08$lbLogin',''\\))\n\nMenu\n\n-   [Home](/)\n-   [Search Contracts](/Search/Search_MainPage.aspx)\n-   [Search Buyers](/Search/Search_Auth.aspx)\n-   [Help and Resources](/helpandresources)\n\n-   [Home](/)\n-   [Search Contracts](/Search/Search_MainPage.aspx)\n-   [Search Buyers](/Search/Search_Auth.aspx)\n-   [Help and Resources](/helpandresources)\n-   [My account](/Membership/Member_ControlPanel.aspx)\n\n# Public sector contract opportunities in Wales\n\n## Search for contracts\n\nKeywords \n\nLocation UK - All ... WALES ...... West Wales and The Valleys ......... Isle of Anglesey ......... Gwynedd ......... Conwy and Denbighshire ......... South West Wales (Carmarthenshire, Pembrokeshire, Ceredigion) ......... Central Valleys (Merthyr Tydfil, Rhondda Cynon Taf) ......... Gwent Valleys (Torfaen, Blaenau Gwent, Caerphilly) ......... Bridgend and Neath Port Talbot ......... Swansea ...... East Wales ......... Monmouthshire and Newport ......... Cardiff and Vale of Glamorgan ......... Flintshire and Wrexham ......... Powys\n\nNotice type All Current Opportunity Future Opportunity Contract Results Pipeline Opportunity\n\n[How to use Sell2Wales?](/helpandresources/additionalinfo/howtousesell2wales)\n\n### Featured\n\n[\n\n#### Search buyers\n\n](/Search/search_Auth.aspx)\n\nSearch our database of over 1200 buyer profile records.\n\n[\n\n#### Manage Sell2Wales notices\n\n](/Authority/Authority_ControlPanel.aspx)\n\nSign in or create an account to add new notices or manage your interest list.\n\n[\n\n#### Projects\n\n](/search/search_CategoryViewList.aspx)\n\nSearch our listing of open projects with details of related notices.\n\n[\n\n#### About Sell2Wales\n\n](/AboutUs/AboutUs_Main.aspx)\n\nWhat is Sell2Wales and who can use the service?\n\n[\n\n#### Open Contracting Transparency Data\n\n](https://www.sell2wales.gov.wales/Notice/Download/Download.aspx)\n\nThe Open Contracting Transparency Data page allows you to download notice information in XML, JSON, XLSX or CSV format.\n\n[\n\n#### Wales Collaborative Procurement Hub\n\n](helpandresources/procurement-resources/walescollaborativeprocurementhub)\n\nThe Wales Collaborative Procurement Hub is an approach to collaborative procurement in Wales.\n\n---\n\n### Latest news\n\n[![Trydan Gwyrdd Cymru - Carmarthenshire Business Breakfast](/Assets/NewsImageProvider.ashx?newsitemid=5682)](/news/news_article.aspx?ID=5682)\n\n#### [Trydan Gwyrdd Cymru - Carmarthenshire Business Breakfast](/news/news_article.aspx?ID=5682)\n\n18 June 2026\n\nTrydan Gwyrdd Cymru - Carmarthenshire Business Breakfast - July 6 2026\n\n[![Is your business involved in delivering a housing scheme in the Carmarthenshire, Neath Port Talbot, ](/Assets/NewsImageProvider.ashx?newsitemid=5665)](/news/news_article.aspx?ID=5665)\n\n#### [Is your business involved in delivering a housing scheme in the Carmarthenshire, Neath Port Talbot,](/news/news_article.aspx?ID=5665)\n\n13 November 2025\n\nIs your business involved in delivering a housing scheme in the Carmarthenshire, Neath Port Talbot, Pembrokeshire or Swansea areas?\n\n[![A new Era for Procurement in Wales](/Assets/NewsImageProvider.ashx?newsitemid=5604)](/news/news_article.aspx?ID=5604)\n\n#### [A new Era for Procurement in Wales](/news/news_article.aspx?ID=5604)\n\n07 March 2025\n\nThe Procurement Act 2023 and associated Welsh regulations have come into force. This is an important milestone in the transformation of public procurement across Wales.\n\n---\n\n[View all news](/News/News_Main.aspx)\n\n---\n\n### Latest Events\n\n---\n\n[View all events](https://wales.business-events.org.uk/)\n\n---\n\n![BOSS Logo](/S2WWeb/Images/BOSS_Logo.png) Business online support service\n\nDigital courses created by Business Wales' subject experts to support you in successfully starting and running a business.\n\n---\n\n### Popular BOSS courses\n\n#### [A greener business](https://boss.businesswales.gov.wales//local/campaign/courseinfo.php?c=A_Greener_Business_-_Busnes_mwy_Gwyrdd&lang=en)\n\nDo you want to know more about going green? Find out how Eco sustainability practices can benefit your business.\n\n#### [The benefits of registering with Sell2Wales](https://boss.businesswales.gov.wales//local/campaign/courseinfo.php?c=The_Benefits_of_Registering_With_Sell2Wales_-_Manteision_Cofrestru_gyda_GwerthwchiGymru&lang=en)\n\nWhy Is Sell2Wales Important to your Business? Learn more about this vital business tool that helps you with information and resources. Gain access to many potential opportunities and contracts.\n\n#### [Pricing your product or service](https://boss.businesswales.gov.wales//local/campaign/courseinfo.php?c=Pricing_Your_Product_or_Service_-_Prisio_eich_Cynnyrch_neu_ch_Gwasanaeth&lang=en)\n\nUnderstand the different ways in which to price your products or services, and what tactics you should consider.\n\n#### [Releasing a new product](https://boss.businesswales.gov.wales//local/campaign/courseinfo.php?c=Releasing_a_New_Product_-_Rhyddhau_Cynnyrch_Newydd&lang=en)\n\nUnderstand what review stages are needed when developing and releasing a new product.\n\n---\n\nFollow Sell2Wales\n\n-   [](https://twitter.com/_Sell2Wales)\n-   [](https://www.facebook.com/Sell2Wales/)\n-   [](https://www.linkedin.com/groups/7498668/)\n-   [](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLG7WQwaaMENg_7vijdMJsLtpmZ4LPap3z)\n-   [](https://www.instagram.com/_business.wales/?hl=en)\n\n---\n\n ![Email icon](/S2WWeb/Images/Icons/email.svg)[Sign up to receive email newsletter](/Membership/Member_Settings.aspx?page=comms)\n\nSell2Wales Helpline\n\n0800 222 9004\n\nLines are open 8:30am to 5pm Monday to Friday.\n\nRydym yn croesawu galwadau'n Gymraeg.\n\nWe welcome calls in Welsh.\n\n[Give feedback about this page](mailto:help@sell2wales.gov.wales?subject=Report%20on%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2Fdefault.aspx&body=Page%20URL%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2Fdefault.aspx%0D%0APage%20title%3A%20Sell2Wales%3A%20Welcome%20to%20Sell2Wales%20-%20Sell2Wales%0D%0AYour%20report%3A%20)\n\n-     ![Share this page](/S2WWeb/Images/Icons/share.svg)Share this page\n    -   [Twitter](http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2fdefault.aspx)\n    -   [Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2fdefault.aspx)\n    -   [E-mail](mailto:?body=https%3a%2f%2fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2fdefault.aspx)\n-   Back to top\n\n-   [About Sell2Wales](/AboutUs/AboutUs_Main.aspx)\n-   [How to use Sell2Wales](/helpandresources/additionalinfo/howtousesell2wales)\n-   [Help and resources](/helpandresources)\n-   [Contact us](/AboutUs/AboutUs_ContactUs.aspx)\n\n---\n\n-   [Cookies](/Cookies/CookiesPolicy.aspx)\n-   [Privacy policy](/helpandresources/websitepolicies/privacypolicy)\n-   [Terms & conditions](/helpandresources/websitepolicies/termsandconditions)\n-   [Accessibility](/SiteHelp/Help_Access.aspx)\n-   [Open Contracting Transparency Data](/Notice/Download/Download.aspx)\n-   [Welsh language policy](/helpandresources/websitepolicies/welsh-language-policy)\n\n-   [![Welsh Government Logo](/S2WWeb/Images/wg-black.svg)](https://gov.wales)\n-   [![Business Wales Logo](/S2WWeb/Images/bw-red.svg)](https://gov.wales)\n\nAll content is available under the Open Government License, except where otherwise stated.",
