 icon](/S2WWeb/Images/Icons/email.svg)[Sign up to receive email newsletter](/Membership/Member_Settings.aspx?page=comms)\n\nSell2Wales Helpline\n\n0800 222 9004\n\nLines are open 8:30am to 5pm Monday to Friday.\n\nRydym yn croesawu galwadau'n Gymraeg.\n\nWe welcome calls in Welsh.\n\n[Give feedback about this page](mailto:help@sell2wales.gov.wales?subject=Report%20on%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2Fhelpandresources%2Fprocurement-resources&body=Page%20URL%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2Fhelpandresources%2Fprocurement-resources%0D%0APage%20title%3A%20Procurement%20resources%20-%20Sell2Wales%0D%0AYour%20report%3A%20)\n\n-     ![Share this page](/S2WWeb/Images/Icons/share.svg)Share this page\n    -   [Twitter](http://twitter.com/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2fhelpandresources%2fprocurement-resources)\n    -   [Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3a%2f%2fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2fhelpandresources%2fprocurement-resources)\n    -   [E-mail](mailto:?body=https%3a%2f%2fwww.sell2wales.gov.wales%2fhelpandresources%2fprocurement-resources)\n-   Back to top\n\n-   [About Sell2Wales](/AboutUs/AboutUs_Main.aspx)\n-   [How to use Sell2Wales](/helpandresources/additionalinfo/howtousesell2wales)\n-   [Help and resources](/helpandresources)\n-   [Contact us](/AboutUs/AboutUs_ContactUs.aspx)\n\n---\n\n-   [Cookies](/Cookies/CookiesPolicy.aspx)\n-   [Privacy policy](/helpandresources/websitepolicies/privacypolicy)\n-   [Terms & conditions](/helpandresources/websitepolicies/termsandconditions)\n-   [Accessibility](/SiteHelp/Help_Access.aspx)\n-   [Open Contracting Transparency Data](/Notice/Download/Download.aspx)\n-   [Welsh language policy](/helpandresources/websitepolicies/welsh-language-policy)\n\n-   [![Welsh Government Logo](/S2WWeb/Images/wg-black.svg)](https://gov.wales)\n-   [![Business Wales Logo](/S2WWeb/Images/bw-red.svg)](https://gov.wales)\n\nAll content is available under the Open Government License, ex