      "output": "                                   Public sector procurement | Sub-topic | GOV.WALES   \n\n[Skip to main content](#wg_main)\n\nGOV.WALES uses cookies which are essential for the site to work. Non-essential cookies are also used to tailor and improve services. By continuing to use this site, you agree to our use of cookies.\n\n[About cookies](/help/cookies)\n\n[Home](https://www.gov.wales/ \"Welsh Government\")![Welsh Government](/themes/custom/govwales/images/print/logo.png)\n\n-   [English](/public-sector-procurement)\n-   [Cymraeg](https://www.llyw.cymru/caffael-yn-y-sector-cyhoeddus)\n\nSearch \n\nYou are here:\n\n-   [Home](/)\n-   [Public sector (Topic)](/public-sector)\n-   Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)\n\nSub-Topic\n\n# Public sector procurement\n\n## In this sub-topic\n\n-   [Guidance and services](#guidance-and-services)\n-   [Policy and background](#policy-and-background)\n-   [Organisations](#organisations)\n\n## Guidance and services\n\n-   [Winning Welsh Government contracts](/winning-welsh-government-contracts)\n    \n-   [How do we manage our procurement of goods and services?](/how-do-we-manage-our-procurement-of-goods-and-services)\n    \n-   [Social Partnership and Public Procurement (Wales) Act](/social-partnership-and-public-procurement-wales-act)\n    \n-   [Smarter public procurement in Wales](/smarter-public-procurement-wales)\n    \n-   [Procurement policy notes](/procurement-policy-notes)\n    \n-   [Procurement Act 2023](/procurement-act-2023)\n    \n-   [Procurement Act 2023: guidance documents](/procurement-act-2023-guidance-documents)\n    \n-   [Procurement Act 2023: templates](/procurement-act-2023-templates)\n    \n-   [The Procurement Act 2023 and Associated Regulations: A short guide for suppliers](/the-procurement-act-2023-and-associated-regulations-a-short-guide-for-suppliers)\n    \n-   [Procurement reform: transparency](/procurement-reform-transparency)\n    \n-   [Bilingual technology toolkit for good user experience](/bilingual-technology-toolkit-good-user-experience)\n    \n-   [Supplier feedback service](/supplier-feedback-service)\n    \n-   [Supplier Feedback Service: guidance for suppliers](/supplier-feedback-service-guidance-for-suppliers)\n    \n-   [Information for Welsh public sector buyers](/information-for-welsh-public-sector-buyers)\n    \n-   [Commercial and Procurement: Learning and development prospectus](/commercial-and-procurement-learning-and-development-prospectus)\n    \n-   [Welsh Revenue Authority conditions for the supply of goods and services](/welsh-revenue-authority-conditions-supply-goods-and-services)\n    \n-   [Welsh Government Procurement Delivery Frameworks](/welsh-government-procurement-delivery-frameworks)\n    \n-   [Ethical employment in supply chains: code of practice, guidance and training](/ethical-employment-supply-chains-code-practice-guidance-and-training)\n    \n-   [Public Contracts Regulations 2015: guidance](/public-contracts-regulations-2015-guidance)\n    \n-   [Procurement pipeline for Welsh public sector](/procurement-pipeline-for-welsh-public-sector)\n    \n-   [Joint bidding for public contracts: guidance for consortia](/joint-bidding-public-contracts-guidance-consortia)\n    \n-   [Joint bidding: online training for bidding consortia](/joint-bidding-online-training-bidding-consortia)\n    \n-   [A toolkit for insourcing in Wales](/a-toolkit-for-insourcing-in-wales)\n    \n-   [Procurement: social value / community benefits](/procurement-social-value-community-benefits)\n    \n-   [Legacy procurement policy notes](/legacy-procurement-policy-notes)\n    \n-   [Contracting authority onboarding](/contracting-authority-onboarding)\n    \n-   [Wales Procurement Review Unit](/wales-procurement-review-unit)\n    \n-   [Wales Procurement Specific Questionnaire (WPSQ)](/wales-procurement-specific-questionnaire)\n    \n-   [Social Partnership handbook](/social-partnership-handbook)\n    \n-   [Health service procurement (