      "output": "                                       Welsh Government’s standard conditions for the supply of services | GOV.WALES   \n\n[Skip to main content](#wg_main)\n\nGOV.WALES uses cookies which are essential for the site to work. Non-essential cookies are also used to tailor and improve services. By continuing to use this site, you agree to our use of cookies.\n\n[About cookies](/help/cookies)\n\n[Home](https://www.gov.wales/ \"Welsh Government\")![Welsh Government](/themes/custom/govwales/images/print/logo.png)\n\n-   [English](/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services)\n-   [Cymraeg](https://www.llyw.cymru/amodau-safonol-llywodraeth-cymru-ar-gyfer-cyflenwi-gwasanaethau)\n\nSearch \n\nYou are here:\n\n-   [Home](/)\n-   [Public sector (Topic)](/public-sector)\n-   [Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)](/public-sector-procurement)\n-   Welsh Government’s standard conditions for the supply of services\n\nPolicy and strategy\n\n# Welsh Government’s standard conditions for the supply of services\n\nStandard terms and conditions we use when awarding procurement contracts.\n\nPart of:\n\n-   [Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)](/public-sector-procurement)\n\nFirst published:\n\n9 October 2019\n\nLast updated:\n\n14 May 2025\n\n## Documents\n\n[\n\n### Standard conditions for the supply of services , file type: PDF, file size: 468 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2025-05/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services.pdf)\n\nPDF\n\n468 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Standard%20conditions%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20services%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Welsh%20Government%E2%80%99s%20standard%20conditions%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20services%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Standard%20conditions%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20services%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20pdf%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2026194%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n## First published\n\n9 October 2019\n\n## Last updated\n\n14 May 2025\n\n## Part of\n\n-   [Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)](/public-sector-procurement)\n\n[Report anything wrong with this page](mailto:digital@gov.wales?url=https%3A//www.gov.wales/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services&subject=Report%20on%20/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services&body=Page%20URL%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services%0APage%20Title%3A%20Welsh%20Government%E2%80%99s%20standard%20conditions%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20services%0AYour%20report%3A%0A)\n\n## Share this page\n\n-   [Share this page via X](https://x.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A//www.gov.wales/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services)\n-   [Share this page via Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.gov.wales/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services)\n-   [Share this page via Email](mailto:?body=https%3A//www.gov.wales/welsh-governments-standard-conditions-supply-services&subject=Shared%20from%20gov.wales)\n\n[Back to top](#brig-top)\n\n-   [Contact us](/contact-us)\n-   [Accessibility](/accessibility-statement-govwales)\n-   [Copyright statement](/copyright-statement)\n-   [Cookies](/help/cookies)\n-   [Privacy](/website-privacy-policy)\n-   [Terms and conditions](/terms-and-conditions)\n-   [Modern slavery statement](/welsh-government-modern-slavery-statement)\n-   [Alternative languages](/alternative-languages)\n\n[Home](https: