      "output": "                                       Procurement Act 2023: templates | GOV.WALES   \n\n[Skip to main content](#wg_main)\n\nGOV.WALES uses cookies which are essential for the site to work. Non-essential cookies are also used to tailor and improve services. By continuing to use this site, you agree to our use of cookies.\n\n[About cookies](/help/cookies)\n\n[Home](https://www.gov.wales/ \"Welsh Government\")![Welsh Government](/themes/custom/govwales/images/print/logo.png)\n\n-   [English](/procurement-act-2023-templates)\n-   [Cymraeg](https://www.llyw.cymru/deddf-caffael-2023-templadau)\n\nSearch \n\nYou are here:\n\n-   [Home](/)\n-   [Public sector (Topic)](/public-sector)\n-   [Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)](/public-sector-procurement)\n-   Procurement Act 2023: templates\n\nForm\n\n# Procurement Act 2023: templates\n\nTender templates for use under the new Act.\n\nPart of:\n\n-   [Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)](/public-sector-procurement)\n\nFirst published:\n\n18 December 2024\n\nLast updated:\n\n21 January 2025\n\n## Documents\n\n[\n\n### Pre-procurement checklist , file type: DOCX, file size: 63 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2024-12/procurement-act-2023-pre-procurement-checklist.docx)\n\nDOCX\n\n63 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Pre-procurement%20checklist%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Pre-procurement%20checklist%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20docx%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2065653%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n[\n\n### Assessment summary: assessed tender , file type: DOCX, file size: 77 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2024-12/procurement-act-2023-assessment-summary-assessed-tender.docx)\n\nDOCX\n\n77 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Assessment%20summary%3A%20assessed%20tender%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Assessment%20summary%3A%20assessed%20tender%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20docx%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2065653%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n[\n\n### Assessment summary: most advantageous tender , file type: DOCX, file size: 63 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2024-12/procurement-act-2023-assessment-summary-most-advantageous-tender.docx)\n\nDOCX\n\n63 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Assessment%20summary%3A%20most%20advantageous%20tender%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Assessment%20summary%3A%20most%20advantageous%20tender%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20docx%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2065653%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n[\n\n### Direct award justification report , file type: DOCX, file size: 83 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2024-12/procurement-act-2023-direct-award-justification-report.docx)\n\nDOCX\n\n83 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Direct%20award%20justification%20report%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Direct%20award%20justification%20report%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20docx%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2065653%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n[\n\n### Conflicts of interest declaration form , file type: DOCX, file size: 70 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2025-01/procurement-act-2023-conflicts-of-interest-declaration-form.docx)\n\nDOCX\n\n70 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Conflicts%20of%20interest%20declaration%20form%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Conflicts%20of%20interest%20declaration%20form%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20docx%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2065653%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n[\n\n### Conflicts assessment , file type: DOCX, file size: 62 KB\n\n\n\n](https://www.gov.wales/sites/default/files/publications/2025-01/procurement-act-2023-conflicts-assessment.docx)\n\nDOCX\n\n62 KB\n\nIf you need a more accessible version of this document please email [digital@gov.wales](mailto:digital@gov.wales?subject=Request%20for%20%27Conflicts%20assessment%27%20in%20an%20alternative%20format&body=Details%20of%20document%20required%3A%0A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0A%20%20Page%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0A%0ARequired%20document%20details%3A%0A%20%20Title%3A%20Conflicts%20assessment%0A%20%20Original%20format%3A%20docx%0A%20%20Unique%20reference%3A%20Node%20ID%2065653%0A%0APlease%20tell%20us%3A%0A%20%201.%20What%20makes%20this%20format%20unsuitable%20for%20you%3F%0A%20%202.%20What%20format%20would%20you%20prefer%3F). Please tell us the format you need. If you use assistive technology please tell us what this is.\n\n## First published\n\n18 December 2024\n\n## Last updated\n\n21 January 2025\n\n## Part of\n\n-   [Public sector procurement (Sub-topic)](/public-sector-procurement)\n\n[Report anything wrong with this page](mailto:digital@gov.wales?url=https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates&subject=Report%20on%20/procurement-act-2023-templates&body=Page%20URL%3A%20https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates%0APage%20Title%3A%20Procurement%20Act%202023%3A%20templates%0AYour%20report%3A%0A)\n\n## Share this page\n\n-   [Share this page via X](https://x.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates)\n-   [Share this page via Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates)\n-   [Share this page via Email](mailto:?body=https%3A//www.gov.wales/procurement-act-2023-templates&subject=Shared%20from%20gov.wales)\n\n[Back to top](#brig-top)\n\n-   [Contact us](/contact-us)\n-   [Accessibility](/accessibility-statement-govwales)\n-   [Copyright statement](/copyright-statement)\n-   [Cookies](/help/cookies)\n-   [Privacy](/website-privacy-policy)\n-   [Terms and conditions](/terms-and-conditions)\n-   [Modern slavery statement](/welsh-government-modern-slavery-statement)\n-   [Alternative languages](/alternative-languages)\n\n[Home](https://www.gov.wales/)",
